2925 PIPE_CONFIG(ADDR_SURF_P8_32x32_8x16) |
2926 TILE_SPLIT(ADDR_SURF_TILE_SPLIT_256B) |
2927 NUM_BANKS(ADDR_SURF_16_BANK) |
2928 BANK_WIDTH(ADDR_SURF_BANK_WIDTH_1) |
2929 BANK_HEIGHT(ADDR_SURF_BANK_HEIGHT_4) |
2930 MACRO_TILE_ASPECT(ADDR_SURF_MACRO_ASPECT_4));
2931 break;
2932 case 23: /* 32 bpp PRT */
2933 gb_tile_moden = (ARRAY_MODE(ARRAY_2D_TILED_THIN1) |
2934 MICRO_TILE_MODE(ADDR_SURF_THIN_MICRO_TILING) |
2935 PIPE_CONFIG(ADDR_SURF_P8_32x32_8x16) |
2936 TILE_SPLIT(ADDR_SURF_TILE_SPLIT_256B) |
2937 NUM_BANKS(ADDR_SURF_16_BANK) |
2938 BANK_WIDTH(ADDR_SURF_BANK_WIDTH_1) |
2939 BANK_HEIGHT(ADDR_SURF_BANK_HEIGHT_2) |
2940 MACRO_TILE_ASPECT(ADDR_SURF_MACRO_ASPECT_2));
2941 break;
2942 case 24: /* 64 bpp PRT */
2943 gb_tile_moden = (ARRAY_MODE(ARRAY_2D_TILED_THIN1) |
2944 MICRO_TILE_MODE(ADDR_SURF_THIN_MICRO_TILING) |
2945 PIPE_CONFIG(ADDR_SURF_P8_32x32_8x16) |
2946 TILE_SPLIT(ADDR_SURF_TILE_SPLIT_512B) |
2947 NUM_BANKS(ADDR_SURF_16_BANK) |
2948 BANK_WIDTH(ADDR_SURF_BANK_WIDTH_1) |
2949 BANK_HEIGHT(ADDR_SURF_BANK_HEIGHT_1) |
2950 MACRO_TILE_ASPECT(ADDR_SURF_MACRO_ASPECT_2));
2951 break;
2952 case 25: /* 128 bpp PRT */
2953 gb_tile_moden = (ARRAY_MODE(ARRAY_2D_TILED_THIN1) |
2954 MICRO_TILE_MODE(ADDR_SURF_THIN_MICRO_TILING) |
2955 PIPE_CONFIG(ADDR_SURF_P8_32x32_8x16) |
2956 TILE_SPLIT(ADDR_SURF_TILE_SPLIT_1KB) |
2957 NUM_BANKS(ADDR_SURF_8_BANK) |
2958 BANK_WIDTH(ADDR_SURF_BANK_WIDTH_1) |
2959 BANK_HEIGHT(ADDR_SURF_BANK_HEIGHT_1) |
2960 MACRO_TILE_ASPECT(ADDR_SURF_MACRO_ASPECT_1));
2961 break;
2962 default:
2963 gb_tile_moden = 0;
2964 break;
2965 }
2966 rdev->config.si.tile_mode_array[reg_offset] = gb_tile_moden;
2967 WREG32(GB_TILE_MODE0 + (reg_offset * 4), gb_tile_moden);
2968 }
2969 } else
2970 DRM_ERROR("unknown asic: 0x%x\n", rdev->family);
2971}
2972
2973static void si_select_se_sh(struct radeon_device *rdev,
2974 u32 se_num, u32 sh_num)
2975{
2976 u32 data = INSTANCE_BROADCAST_WRITES;
2977
2978 if ((se_num == 0xffffffff) && (sh_num == 0xffffffff))
2979 data |= SH_BROADCAST_WRITES | SE_BROADCAST_WRITES;
2980 else if (se_num == 0xffffffff)
2981 data |= SE_BROADCAST_WRITES | SH_INDEX(sh_num);
2982 else if (sh_num == 0xffffffff)
2983 data |= SH_BROADCAST_WRITES | SE_INDEX(se_num);
2984 else
2985 data |= SH_INDEX(sh_num) | SE_INDEX(se_num);
2986 WREG32(GRBM_GFX_INDEX, data);
2987}
2988
2989static u32 si_create_bitmask(u32 bit_width)
2990{
2991 u32 i, mask = 0;
2992
2993 for (i = 0; i < bit_width; i++) {
2994 mask <<= 1;
2995 mask |= 1;
2996 }
2997 return mask;
2998}
2999
3000static u32 si_get_cu_enabled(struct radeon_device *rdev, u32 cu_per_sh)
3001{
3002 u32 data, mask;
3003
3004 data = RREG32(CC_GC_SHADER_ARRAY_CONFIG);
3005 if (data & 1)
3006 data &= INACTIVE_CUS_MASK;
3007 else
3008 data = 0;
3009 data |= RREG32(GC_USER_SHADER_ARRAY_CONFIG);
3010
3011 data >>= INACTIVE_CUS_SHIFT;
3012
3013 mask = si_create_bitmask(cu_per_sh);
3014
3015 return ~data & mask;
3016}
3017
3018static void si_setup_spi(struct radeon_device *rdev,
3019 u32 se_num, u32 sh_per_se,
3020 u32 cu_per_sh)
3021{
3022 int i, j, k;
3023 u32 data, mask, active_cu;
3024
3025 for (i = 0; i < se_num; i++) {
3026 for (j = 0; j < sh_per_se; j++) {
3027 si_select_se_sh(rdev, i, j);
3028 data = RREG32(SPI_STATIC_THREAD_MGMT_3);
3029 active_cu = si_get_cu_enabled(rdev, cu_per_sh);
3030
3031 mask = 1;
3032 for (k = 0; k < 16; k++) {
3033 mask <<= k;
3034 if (active_cu & mask) {
3035 data &= ~mask;
3036 WREG32(SPI_STATIC_THREAD_MGMT_3, data);
3037 break;
3038 }
3039 }
3040 }
3041 }
3042 si_select_se_sh(rdev, 0xffffffff, 0xffffffff);
3043}
3044
3045static u32 si_get_rb_disabled(struct radeon_device *rdev,
3046 u32 max_rb_num_per_se,
3047 u32 sh_per_se)
3048{
3049 u32 data, mask;
3050
3051 data = RREG32(CC_RB_BACKEND_DISABLE);
3052 if (data & 1)
3053 data &= BACKEND_DISABLE_MASK;
3054 else
3055 data = 0;
3056 data |= RREG32(GC_USER_RB_BACKEND_DISABLE);
3057
3058 data >>= BACKEND_DISABLE_SHIFT;
3059
3060 mask = si_create_bitmask(max_rb_num_per_se / sh_per_se);
3061
3062 return data & mask;
3063}
3064
3065static void si_setup_rb(struct radeon_device *rdev,
3066 u32 se_num, u32 sh_per_se,
3067 u32 max_rb_num_per_se)
3068{
3069 int i, j;
3070 u32 data, mask;
3071 u32 disabled_rbs = 0;
3072 u32 enabled_rbs = 0;
3073
3074 for (i = 0; i < se_num; i++) {
3075 for (j = 0; j < sh_per_se; j++) {
3076 si_select_se_sh(rdev, i, j);
3077 data = si_get_rb_disabled(rdev, max_rb_num_per_se, sh_per_se);
3078 disabled_rbs |= data << ((i * sh_per_se + j) * TAHITI_RB_BITMAP_WIDTH_PER_SH);
3079 }
3080 }
3081 si_select_se_sh(rdev, 0xffffffff, 0xffffffff);
3082
3083 mask = 1;
3084 for (i = 0; i < max_rb_num_per_se * se_num; i++) {
3085 if (!(disabled_rbs & mask))
3086 enabled_rbs |= mask;
3087 mask <<= 1;
3088 }
3089
3090 rdev->config.si.backend_enable_mask = enabled_rbs;
3091
3092 for (i = 0; i < se_num; i++) {
3093 si_select_se_sh(rdev, i, 0xffffffff);
3094 data = 0;
3095 for (j = 0; j < sh_per_se; j++) {
3096 switch (enabled_rbs & 3) {
3097 case 1:
3098 data |= (RASTER_CONFIG_RB_MAP_0 << (i * sh_per_se + j) * 2);
3099 break;
3100 case 2:
3101 data |= (RASTER_CONFIG_RB_MAP_3 << (i * sh_per_se + j) * 2);
3102 break;
3103 case 3:
3104 default:
3105 data |= (RASTER_CONFIG_RB_MAP_2 << (i * sh_per_se + j) * 2);
3106 break;
3107 }
3108 enabled_rbs >>= 2;
3109 }
3110 WREG32(PA_SC_RASTER_CONFIG, data);
3111 }
3112 si_select_se_sh(rdev, 0xffffffff, 0xffffffff);
3113}
3114
3115static void si_gpu_init(struct radeon_device *rdev)
3116{
3117 u32 gb_addr_config = 0;
3118 u32 mc_shared_chmap __unused, mc_arb_ramcfg;
3119 u32 sx_debug_1;
3120 u32 hdp_host_path_cntl;
3121 u32 tmp;
3122 int i, j;
3123
3124 switch (rdev->family) {
3125 case CHIP_TAHITI:
3126 rdev->config.si.max_shader_engines = 2;
3127 rdev->config.si.max_tile_pipes = 12;
3128 rdev->config.si.max_cu_per_sh = 8;
3129 rdev->config.si.max_sh_per_se = 2;
3130 rdev->config.si.max_backends_per_se = 4;
3131 rdev->config.si.max_texture_channel_caches = 12;
3132 rdev->config.si.max_gprs = 256;
3133 rdev->config.si.max_gs_threads = 32;
3134 rdev->config.si.max_hw_contexts = 8;
3135
3136 rdev->config.si.sc_prim_fifo_size_frontend = 0x20;
3137 rdev->config.si.sc_prim_fifo_size_backend = 0x100;
3138 rdev->config.si.sc_hiz_tile_fifo_size = 0x30;
3139 rdev->config.si.sc_earlyz_tile_fifo_size = 0x130;
3140 gb_addr_config = TAHITI_GB_ADDR_CONFIG_GOLDEN;
3141 break;
3142 case CHIP_PITCAIRN:
3143 rdev->config.si.max_shader_engines = 2;
3144 rdev->config.si.max_tile_pipes = 8;
3145 rdev->config.si.max_cu_per_sh = 5;
3146 rdev->config.si.max_sh_per_se = 2;
3147 rdev->config.si.max_backends_per_se = 4;
3148 rdev->config.si.max_texture_channel_caches = 8;
3149 rdev->config.si.max_gprs = 256;
3150 rdev->config.si.max_gs_threads = 32;
3151 rdev->config.si.max_hw_contexts = 8;
3152
3153 rdev->config.si.sc_prim_fifo_size_frontend = 0x20;
3154 rdev->config.si.sc_prim_fifo_size_backend = 0x100;
3155 rdev->config.si.sc_hiz_tile_fifo_size = 0x30;
3156 rdev->config.si.sc_earlyz_tile_fifo_size = 0x130;
3157 gb_addr_config = TAHITI_GB_ADDR_CONFIG_GOLDEN;
3158 break;
3159 case CHIP_VERDE:
3160 default:
3161 rdev->config.si.max_shader_engines = 1;
3162 rdev->config.si.max_tile_pipes = 4;
3163 rdev->config.si.max_cu_per_sh = 5;
3164 rdev->config.si.max_sh_per_se = 2;
3165 rdev->config.si.max_backends_per_se = 4;
3166 rdev->config.si.max_texture_channel_caches = 4;
3167 rdev->config.si.max_gprs = 256;
3168 rdev->config.si.max_gs_threads = 32;
3169 rdev->config.si.max_hw_contexts = 8;
3170
3171 rdev->config.si.sc_prim_fifo_size_frontend = 0x20;
3172 rdev->config.si.sc_prim_fifo_size_backend = 0x40;
3173 rdev->config.si.sc_hiz_tile_fifo_size = 0x30;
3174 rdev->config.si.sc_earlyz_tile_fifo_size = 0x130;
3175 gb_addr_config = VERDE_GB_ADDR_CONFIG_GOLDEN;
3176 break;
3177 case CHIP_OLAND:
3178 rdev->config.si.max_shader_engines = 1;
3179 rdev->config.si.max_tile_pipes = 4;
3180 rdev->config.si.max_cu_per_sh = 6;
3181 rdev->config.si.max_sh_per_se = 1;
3182 rdev->config.si.max_backends_per_se = 2;
3183 rdev->config.si.max_texture_channel_caches = 4;
3184 rdev->config.si.max_gprs = 256;
3185 rdev->config.si.max_gs_threads = 16;
3186 rdev->config.si.max_hw_contexts = 8;
3187
3188 rdev->config.si.sc_prim_fifo_size_frontend = 0x20;
3189 rdev->config.si.sc_prim_fifo_size_backend = 0x40;
3190 rdev->config.si.sc_hiz_tile_fifo_size = 0x30;
3191 rdev->config.si.sc_earlyz_tile_fifo_size = 0x130;
3192 gb_addr_config = VERDE_GB_ADDR_CONFIG_GOLDEN;
3193 break;
3194 case CHIP_HAINAN:
3195 rdev->config.si.max_shader_engines = 1;
3196 rdev->config.si.max_tile_pipes = 4;
3197 rdev->config.si.max_cu_per_sh = 5;
3198 rdev->config.si.max_sh_per_se = 1;
3199 rdev->config.si.max_backends_per_se = 1;
3200 rdev->config.si.max_texture_channel_caches = 2;
3201 rdev->config.si.max_gprs = 256;
3202 rdev->config.si.max_gs_threads = 16;
3203 rdev->config.si.max_hw_contexts = 8;
3204
3205 rdev->config.si.sc_prim_fifo_size_frontend = 0x20;
3206 rdev->config.si.sc_prim_fifo_size_backend = 0x40;
3207 rdev->config.si.sc_hiz_tile_fifo_size = 0x30;
3208 rdev->config.si.sc_earlyz_tile_fifo_size = 0x130;
3209 gb_addr_config = HAINAN_GB_ADDR_CONFIG_GOLDEN;
3210 break;
3211 }
3212
3213 /* Initialize HDP */
3214 for (i = 0, j = 0; i < 32; i++, j += 0x18) {
3215 WREG32((0x2c14 + j), 0x00000000);
3216 WREG32((0x2c18 + j), 0x00000000);
3217 WREG32((0x2c1c + j), 0x00000000);
3218 WREG32((0x2c20 + j), 0x00000000);
3219 WREG32((0x2c24 + j), 0x00000000);
3220 }
3221
3222 WREG32(GRBM_CNTL, GRBM_READ_TIMEOUT(0xff));
3223 WREG32(SRBM_INT_CNTL, 1);
3224 WREG32(SRBM_INT_ACK, 1);
3225
3226 evergreen_fix_pci_max_read_req_size(rdev);
3227
3228 WREG32(BIF_FB_EN, FB_READ_EN | FB_WRITE_EN);
3229
3230 mc_shared_chmap = RREG32(MC_SHARED_CHMAP);
3231 mc_arb_ramcfg = RREG32(MC_ARB_RAMCFG);
3232
3233 rdev->config.si.num_tile_pipes = rdev->config.si.max_tile_pipes;
3234 rdev->config.si.mem_max_burst_length_bytes = 256;
3235 tmp = (mc_arb_ramcfg & NOOFCOLS_MASK) >> NOOFCOLS_SHIFT;
3236 rdev->config.si.mem_row_size_in_kb = (4 * (1 << (8 + tmp))) / 1024;
3237 if (rdev->config.si.mem_row_size_in_kb > 4)
3238 rdev->config.si.mem_row_size_in_kb = 4;
3239 /* XXX use MC settings? */
3240 rdev->config.si.shader_engine_tile_size = 32;
3241 rdev->config.si.num_gpus = 1;
3242 rdev->config.si.multi_gpu_tile_size = 64;
3243
3244 /* fix up row size */
3245 gb_addr_config &= ~ROW_SIZE_MASK;
3246 switch (rdev->config.si.mem_row_size_in_kb) {
3247 case 1:
3248 default:
3249 gb_addr_config |= ROW_SIZE(0);
3250 break;
3251 case 2:
3252 gb_addr_config |= ROW_SIZE(1);
3253 break;
3254 case 4:
3255 gb_addr_config |= ROW_SIZE(2);
3256 break;
3257 }
3258
3259 /* setup tiling info dword. gb_addr_config is not adequate since it does
3260 * not have bank info, so create a custom tiling dword.
3261 * bits 3:0 num_pipes
3262 * bits 7:4 num_banks
3263 * bits 11:8 group_size
3264 * bits 15:12 row_size
3265 */
3266 rdev->config.si.tile_config = 0;
3267 switch (rdev->config.si.num_tile_pipes) {
3268 case 1:
3269 rdev->config.si.tile_config |= (0 << 0);
3270 break;
3271 case 2:
3272 rdev->config.si.tile_config |= (1 << 0);
3273 break;
3274 case 4:
3275 rdev->config.si.tile_config |= (2 << 0);
3276 break;
3277 case 8:
3278 default:
3279 /* XXX what about 12? */
3280 rdev->config.si.tile_config |= (3 << 0);
3281 break;
3282 }
3283 switch ((mc_arb_ramcfg & NOOFBANK_MASK) >> NOOFBANK_SHIFT) {
3284 case 0: /* four banks */
3285 rdev->config.si.tile_config |= 0 << 4;
3286 break;
3287 case 1: /* eight banks */
3288 rdev->config.si.tile_config |= 1 << 4;
3289 break;
3290 case 2: /* sixteen banks */
3291 default:
3292 rdev->config.si.tile_config |= 2 << 4;
3293 break;
3294 }
3295 rdev->config.si.tile_config |=
3296 ((gb_addr_config & PIPE_INTERLEAVE_SIZE_MASK) >> PIPE_INTERLEAVE_SIZE_SHIFT) << 8;
3297 rdev->config.si.tile_config |=
3298 ((gb_addr_config & ROW_SIZE_MASK) >> ROW_SIZE_SHIFT) << 12;
3299
3300 WREG32(GB_ADDR_CONFIG, gb_addr_config);
3301 WREG32(DMIF_ADDR_CONFIG, gb_addr_config);
3302 WREG32(DMIF_ADDR_CALC, gb_addr_config);
3303 WREG32(HDP_ADDR_CONFIG, gb_addr_config);
3304 WREG32(DMA_TILING_CONFIG + DMA0_REGISTER_OFFSET, gb_addr_config);
3305 WREG32(DMA_TILING_CONFIG + DMA1_REGISTER_OFFSET, gb_addr_config);
3306 if (rdev->has_uvd) {
3307 WREG32(UVD_UDEC_ADDR_CONFIG, gb_addr_config);
3308 WREG32(UVD_UDEC_DB_ADDR_CONFIG, gb_addr_config);
3309 WREG32(UVD_UDEC_DBW_ADDR_CONFIG, gb_addr_config);
3310 }
3311
3312 si_tiling_mode_table_init(rdev);
3313
3314 si_setup_rb(rdev, rdev->config.si.max_shader_engines,
3315 rdev->config.si.max_sh_per_se,
3316 rdev->config.si.max_backends_per_se);
3317
3318 si_setup_spi(rdev, rdev->config.si.max_shader_engines,
3319 rdev->config.si.max_sh_per_se,
3320 rdev->config.si.max_cu_per_sh);
3321
3322 rdev->config.si.active_cus = 0;
3323 for (i = 0; i < rdev->config.si.max_shader_engines; i++) {
3324 for (j = 0; j < rdev->config.si.max_sh_per_se; j++) {
3325 rdev->config.si.active_cus +=
3326 hweight32(si_get_cu_active_bitmap(rdev, i, j));
3327 }
3328 }
3329
3330 /* set HW defaults for 3D engine */
3331 WREG32(CP_QUEUE_THRESHOLDS, (ROQ_IB1_START(0x16) |
3332 ROQ_IB2_START(0x2b)));
3333 WREG32(CP_MEQ_THRESHOLDS, MEQ1_START(0x30) | MEQ2_START(0x60));
3334
3335 sx_debug_1 = RREG32(SX_DEBUG_1);
3336 WREG32(SX_DEBUG_1, sx_debug_1);
3337
3338 WREG32(SPI_CONFIG_CNTL_1, VTX_DONE_DELAY(4));
3339
3340 WREG32(PA_SC_FIFO_SIZE, (SC_FRONTEND_PRIM_FIFO_SIZE(rdev->config.si.sc_prim_fifo_size_frontend) |
3341 SC_BACKEND_PRIM_FIFO_SIZE(rdev->config.si.sc_prim_fifo_size_backend) |
3342 SC_HIZ_TILE_FIFO_SIZE(rdev->config.si.sc_hiz_tile_fifo_size) |
3343 SC_EARLYZ_TILE_FIFO_SIZE(rdev->config.si.sc_earlyz_tile_fifo_size)));
3344
3345 WREG32(VGT_NUM_INSTANCES, 1);
3346
3347 WREG32(CP_PERFMON_CNTL, 0);
3348
3349 WREG32(SQ_CONFIG, 0);
3350
3351 WREG32(PA_SC_FORCE_EOV_MAX_CNTS, (FORCE_EOV_MAX_CLK_CNT(4095) |
3352 FORCE_EOV_MAX_REZ_CNT(255)));
3353
3354 WREG32(VGT_CACHE_INVALIDATION, CACHE_INVALIDATION(VC_AND_TC) |
3355 AUTO_INVLD_EN(ES_AND_GS_AUTO));
3356
3357 WREG32(VGT_GS_VERTEX_REUSE, 16);
3358 WREG32(PA_SC_LINE_STIPPLE_STATE, 0);
3359
3360 WREG32(CB_PERFCOUNTER0_SELECT0, 0);
3361 WREG32(CB_PERFCOUNTER0_SELECT1, 0);
3362 WREG32(CB_PERFCOUNTER1_SELECT0, 0);
3363 WREG32(CB_PERFCOUNTER1_SELECT1, 0);
3364 WREG32(CB_PERFCOUNTER2_SELECT0, 0);
3365 WREG32(CB_PERFCOUNTER2_SELECT1, 0);
3366 WREG32(CB_PERFCOUNTER3_SELECT0, 0);
3367 WREG32(CB_PERFCOUNTER3_SELECT1, 0);
3368
3369 tmp = RREG32(HDP_MISC_CNTL);
3370 tmp |= HDP_FLUSH_INVALIDATE_CACHE;
3371 WREG32(HDP_MISC_CNTL, tmp);
3372
3373 hdp_host_path_cntl = RREG32(HDP_HOST_PATH_CNTL);
3374 WREG32(HDP_HOST_PATH_CNTL, hdp_host_path_cntl);
3375
3376 WREG32(PA_CL_ENHANCE, CLIP_VTX_REORDER_ENA | NUM_CLIP_SEQ(3));
3377
3378 udelay(50);
3379}
3380
3381/*
3382 * GPU scratch registers helpers function.
3383 */
3384static void si_scratch_init(struct radeon_device *rdev)
3385{
3386 int i;
3387
3388 rdev->scratch.num_reg = 7;
3389 rdev->scratch.reg_base = SCRATCH_REG0;
3390 for (i = 0; i < rdev->scratch.num_reg; i++) {
3391 rdev->scratch.free[i] = true;
3392 rdev->scratch.reg[i] = rdev->scratch.reg_base + (i * 4);
3393 }
3394}
3395
3396void si_fence_ring_emit(struct radeon_device *rdev,
3397 struct radeon_fence *fence)
3398{
3399 struct radeon_ring *ring = &rdev->ring[fence->ring];
3400 u64 addr = rdev->fence_drv[fence->ring].gpu_addr;
3401
3402 /* flush read cache over gart */
3403 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_SET_CONFIG_REG, 1));
3404 radeon_ring_write(ring, (CP_COHER_CNTL2 - PACKET3_SET_CONFIG_REG_START) >> 2);
3405 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
3406 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_SURFACE_SYNC, 3));
3407 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3_TCL1_ACTION_ENA |
3408 PACKET3_TC_ACTION_ENA |
3409 PACKET3_SH_KCACHE_ACTION_ENA |
3410 PACKET3_SH_ICACHE_ACTION_ENA);
3411 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0xFFFFFFFF);
3412 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
3413 radeon_ring_write(ring, 10); /* poll interval */
3414 /* EVENT_WRITE_EOP - flush caches, send int */
3415 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_EVENT_WRITE_EOP, 4));
3416 radeon_ring_write(ring, EVENT_TYPE(CACHE_FLUSH_AND_INV_TS_EVENT) | EVENT_INDEX(5));
3417 radeon_ring_write(ring, lower_32_bits(addr));
3418 radeon_ring_write(ring, (upper_32_bits(addr) & 0xff) | DATA_SEL(1) | INT_SEL(2));
3419 radeon_ring_write(ring, fence->seq);
3420 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
3421}
3422
3423/*
3424 * IB stuff
3425 */
3426void si_ring_ib_execute(struct radeon_device *rdev, struct radeon_ib *ib)
3427{
3428 struct radeon_ring *ring = &rdev->ring[ib->ring];
3429 unsigned vm_id = ib->vm ? ib->vm->ids[ib->ring].id : 0;
3430 u32 header;
3431
3432 if (ib->is_const_ib) {
3433 /* set switch buffer packet before const IB */
3434 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_SWITCH_BUFFER, 0));
3435 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
3436
3437 header = PACKET3(PACKET3_INDIRECT_BUFFER_CONST, 2);
3438 } else {
3439 u32 next_rptr;
3440 if (ring->rptr_save_reg) {
3441 next_rptr = ring->wptr + 3 + 4 + 8;
3442 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_SET_CONFIG_REG, 1));
3443 radeon_ring_write(ring, ((ring->rptr_save_reg -
3444 PACKET3_SET_CONFIG_REG_START) >> 2));
3445 radeon_ring_write(ring, next_rptr);
3446 } else if (rdev->wb.enabled) {
3447 next_rptr = ring->wptr + 5 + 4 + 8;
3448 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_WRITE_DATA, 3));
3449 radeon_ring_write(ring, (1 << 8));
3450 radeon_ring_write(ring, ring->next_rptr_gpu_addr & 0xfffffffc);
3451 radeon_ring_write(ring, upper_32_bits(ring->next_rptr_gpu_addr));
3452 radeon_ring_write(ring, next_rptr);
3453 }
3454
3455 header = PACKET3(PACKET3_INDIRECT_BUFFER, 2);
3456 }
3457
3458 radeon_ring_write(ring, header);
3459 radeon_ring_write(ring,
3460#ifdef __BIG_ENDIAN
3461 (2 << 0) |
3462#endif
3463 (ib->gpu_addr & 0xFFFFFFFC));
3464 radeon_ring_write(ring, upper_32_bits(ib->gpu_addr) & 0xFFFF);
3465 radeon_ring_write(ring, ib->length_dw | (vm_id << 24));
3466
3467 if (!ib->is_const_ib) {
3468 /* flush read cache over gart for this vmid */
3469 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_SET_CONFIG_REG, 1));
3470 radeon_ring_write(ring, (CP_COHER_CNTL2 - PACKET3_SET_CONFIG_REG_START) >> 2);
3471 radeon_ring_write(ring, vm_id);
3472 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_SURFACE_SYNC, 3));
3473 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3_TCL1_ACTION_ENA |
3474 PACKET3_TC_ACTION_ENA |
3475 PACKET3_SH_KCACHE_ACTION_ENA |
3476 PACKET3_SH_ICACHE_ACTION_ENA);
3477 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0xFFFFFFFF);
3478 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
3479 radeon_ring_write(ring, 10); /* poll interval */
3480 }
3481}
3482
3483/*
3484 * CP.
3485 */
3486static void si_cp_enable(struct radeon_device *rdev, bool enable)
3487{
3488 if (enable)
3489 WREG32(CP_ME_CNTL, 0);
3490 else {
3491 if (rdev->asic->copy.copy_ring_index == RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX)
3492 radeon_ttm_set_active_vram_size(rdev, rdev->mc.visible_vram_size);
3493 WREG32(CP_ME_CNTL, (CP_ME_HALT | CP_PFP_HALT | CP_CE_HALT));
3494 WREG32(SCRATCH_UMSK, 0);
3495 rdev->ring[RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX].ready = false;
3496 rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX].ready = false;
3497 rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX].ready = false;
3498 }
3499 udelay(50);
3500}
3501
3502static int si_cp_load_microcode(struct radeon_device *rdev)
3503{
3504 int i;
3505
3506 if (!rdev->me_fw || !rdev->pfp_fw || !rdev->ce_fw)
3507 return -EINVAL;
3508
3509 si_cp_enable(rdev, false);
3510
3511 if (rdev->new_fw) {
3512 const struct gfx_firmware_header_v1_0 *pfp_hdr =
3513 (const struct gfx_firmware_header_v1_0 *)rdev->pfp_fw->data;
3514 const struct gfx_firmware_header_v1_0 *ce_hdr =
3515 (const struct gfx_firmware_header_v1_0 *)rdev->ce_fw->data;
3516 const struct gfx_firmware_header_v1_0 *me_hdr =
3517 (const struct gfx_firmware_header_v1_0 *)rdev->me_fw->data;
3518 const __le32 *fw_data;
3519 u32 fw_size;
3520
3521 radeon_ucode_print_gfx_hdr(&pfp_hdr->header);
3522 radeon_ucode_print_gfx_hdr(&ce_hdr->header);
3523 radeon_ucode_print_gfx_hdr(&me_hdr->header);
3524
3525 /* PFP */
3526 fw_data = (const __le32 *)
3527 (rdev->pfp_fw->data + le32_to_cpu(pfp_hdr->header.ucode_array_offset_bytes));
3528 fw_size = le32_to_cpu(pfp_hdr->header.ucode_size_bytes) / 4;
3529 WREG32(CP_PFP_UCODE_ADDR, 0);
3530 for (i = 0; i < fw_size; i++)
3531 WREG32(CP_PFP_UCODE_DATA, le32_to_cpup(fw_data++));
3532 WREG32(CP_PFP_UCODE_ADDR, 0);
3533
3534 /* CE */
3535 fw_data = (const __le32 *)
3536 (rdev->ce_fw->data + le32_to_cpu(ce_hdr->header.ucode_array_offset_bytes));
3537 fw_size = le32_to_cpu(ce_hdr->header.ucode_size_bytes) / 4;
3538 WREG32(CP_CE_UCODE_ADDR, 0);
3539 for (i = 0; i < fw_size; i++)
3540 WREG32(CP_CE_UCODE_DATA, le32_to_cpup(fw_data++));
3541 WREG32(CP_CE_UCODE_ADDR, 0);
3542
3543 /* ME */
3544 fw_data = (const __be32 *)
3545 (rdev->me_fw->data + le32_to_cpu(me_hdr->header.ucode_array_offset_bytes));
3546 fw_size = le32_to_cpu(me_hdr->header.ucode_size_bytes) / 4;
3547 WREG32(CP_ME_RAM_WADDR, 0);
3548 for (i = 0; i < fw_size; i++)
3549 WREG32(CP_ME_RAM_DATA, le32_to_cpup(fw_data++));
3550 WREG32(CP_ME_RAM_WADDR, 0);
3551 } else {
3552 const __be32 *fw_data;
3553
3554 /* PFP */
3555 fw_data = (const __be32 *)rdev->pfp_fw->data;
3556 WREG32(CP_PFP_UCODE_ADDR, 0);
3557 for (i = 0; i < SI_PFP_UCODE_SIZE; i++)
3558 WREG32(CP_PFP_UCODE_DATA, be32_to_cpup(fw_data++));
3559 WREG32(CP_PFP_UCODE_ADDR, 0);
3560
3561 /* CE */
3562 fw_data = (const __be32 *)rdev->ce_fw->data;
3563 WREG32(CP_CE_UCODE_ADDR, 0);
3564 for (i = 0; i < SI_CE_UCODE_SIZE; i++)
3565 WREG32(CP_CE_UCODE_DATA, be32_to_cpup(fw_data++));
3566 WREG32(CP_CE_UCODE_ADDR, 0);
3567
3568 /* ME */
3569 fw_data = (const __be32 *)rdev->me_fw->data;
3570 WREG32(CP_ME_RAM_WADDR, 0);
3571 for (i = 0; i < SI_PM4_UCODE_SIZE; i++)
3572 WREG32(CP_ME_RAM_DATA, be32_to_cpup(fw_data++));
3573 WREG32(CP_ME_RAM_WADDR, 0);
3574 }
3575
3576 WREG32(CP_PFP_UCODE_ADDR, 0);
3577 WREG32(CP_CE_UCODE_ADDR, 0);
3578 WREG32(CP_ME_RAM_WADDR, 0);
3579 WREG32(CP_ME_RAM_RADDR, 0);
3580 return 0;
3581}
3582
3583static int si_cp_start(struct radeon_device *rdev)
3584{
3585 struct radeon_ring *ring = &rdev->ring[RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX];
3586 int r, i;
3587
3588 r = radeon_ring_lock(rdev, ring, 7 + 4);
3589 if (r) {
3590 DRM_ERROR("radeon: cp failed to lock ring (%d).\n", r);
3591 return r;
3592 }
3593 /* init the CP */
3594 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_ME_INITIALIZE, 5));
3595 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0x1);
3596 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0x0);
3597 radeon_ring_write(ring, rdev->config.si.max_hw_contexts - 1);
3598 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3_ME_INITIALIZE_DEVICE_ID(1));
3599 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
3600 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
3601
3602 /* init the CE partitions */
3603 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_SET_BASE, 2));
3604 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3_BASE_INDEX(CE_PARTITION_BASE));
3605 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0xc000);
3606 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0xe000);
3607 radeon_ring_unlock_commit(rdev, ring, false);
3608
3609 si_cp_enable(rdev, true);
3610
3611 r = radeon_ring_lock(rdev, ring, si_default_size + 10);
3612 if (r) {
3613 DRM_ERROR("radeon: cp failed to lock ring (%d).\n", r);
3614 return r;
3615 }
3616
3617 /* setup clear context state */
3618 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_PREAMBLE_CNTL, 0));
3619 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3_PREAMBLE_BEGIN_CLEAR_STATE);
3620
3621 for (i = 0; i < si_default_size; i++)
3622 radeon_ring_write(ring, si_default_state[i]);
3623
3624 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_PREAMBLE_CNTL, 0));
3625 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3_PREAMBLE_END_CLEAR_STATE);
3626
3627 /* set clear context state */
3628 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_CLEAR_STATE, 0));
3629 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
3630
3631 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_SET_CONTEXT_REG, 2));
3632 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0x00000316);
3633 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0x0000000e); /* VGT_VERTEX_REUSE_BLOCK_CNTL */
3634 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0x00000010); /* VGT_OUT_DEALLOC_CNTL */
3635
3636 radeon_ring_unlock_commit(rdev, ring, false);
3637
3638 for (i = RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX; i <= CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX; ++i) {
3639 ring = &rdev->ring[i];
3640 r = radeon_ring_lock(rdev, ring, 2);
3641
3642 /* clear the compute context state */
3643 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3_COMPUTE(PACKET3_CLEAR_STATE, 0));
3644 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
3645
3646 radeon_ring_unlock_commit(rdev, ring, false);
3647 }
3648
3649 return 0;
3650}
3651
3652static void si_cp_fini(struct radeon_device *rdev)
3653{
3654 struct radeon_ring *ring;
3655 si_cp_enable(rdev, false);
3656
3657 ring = &rdev->ring[RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX];
3658 radeon_ring_fini(rdev, ring);
3659 radeon_scratch_free(rdev, ring->rptr_save_reg);
3660
3661 ring = &rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX];
3662 radeon_ring_fini(rdev, ring);
3663 radeon_scratch_free(rdev, ring->rptr_save_reg);
3664
3665 ring = &rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX];
3666 radeon_ring_fini(rdev, ring);
3667 radeon_scratch_free(rdev, ring->rptr_save_reg);
3668}
3669
3670static int si_cp_resume(struct radeon_device *rdev)
3671{
3672 struct radeon_ring *ring;
3673 u32 tmp;
3674 u32 rb_bufsz;
3675 int r;
3676
3677 si_enable_gui_idle_interrupt(rdev, false);
3678
3679 WREG32(CP_SEM_WAIT_TIMER, 0x0);
3680 WREG32(CP_SEM_INCOMPLETE_TIMER_CNTL, 0x0);
3681
3682 /* Set the write pointer delay */
3683 WREG32(CP_RB_WPTR_DELAY, 0);
3684
3685 WREG32(CP_DEBUG, 0);
3686 WREG32(SCRATCH_ADDR, ((rdev->wb.gpu_addr + RADEON_WB_SCRATCH_OFFSET) >> 8) & 0xFFFFFFFF);
3687
3688 /* ring 0 - compute and gfx */
3689 /* Set ring buffer size */
3690 ring = &rdev->ring[RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX];
3691 rb_bufsz = order_base_2(ring->ring_size / 8);
3692 tmp = (order_base_2(RADEON_GPU_PAGE_SIZE/8) << 8) | rb_bufsz;
3693#ifdef __BIG_ENDIAN
3694 tmp |= BUF_SWAP_32BIT;
3695#endif
3696 WREG32(CP_RB0_CNTL, tmp);
3697
3698 /* Initialize the ring buffer's read and write pointers */
3699 WREG32(CP_RB0_CNTL, tmp | RB_RPTR_WR_ENA);
3700 ring->wptr = 0;
3701 WREG32(CP_RB0_WPTR, ring->wptr);
3702
3703 /* set the wb address whether it's enabled or not */
3704 WREG32(CP_RB0_RPTR_ADDR, (rdev->wb.gpu_addr + RADEON_WB_CP_RPTR_OFFSET) & 0xFFFFFFFC);
3705 WREG32(CP_RB0_RPTR_ADDR_HI, upper_32_bits(rdev->wb.gpu_addr + RADEON_WB_CP_RPTR_OFFSET) & 0xFF);
3706
3707 if (rdev->wb.enabled)
3708 WREG32(SCRATCH_UMSK, 0xff);
3709 else {
3710 tmp |= RB_NO_UPDATE;
3711 WREG32(SCRATCH_UMSK, 0);
3712 }
3713
3714 mdelay(1);
3715 WREG32(CP_RB0_CNTL, tmp);
3716
3717 WREG32(CP_RB0_BASE, ring->gpu_addr >> 8);
3718
3719 /* ring1 - compute only */
3720 /* Set ring buffer size */
3721 ring = &rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX];
3722 rb_bufsz = order_base_2(ring->ring_size / 8);
3723 tmp = (order_base_2(RADEON_GPU_PAGE_SIZE/8) << 8) | rb_bufsz;
3724#ifdef __BIG_ENDIAN
3725 tmp |= BUF_SWAP_32BIT;
3726#endif
3727 WREG32(CP_RB1_CNTL, tmp);
3728
3729 /* Initialize the ring buffer's read and write pointers */
3730 WREG32(CP_RB1_CNTL, tmp | RB_RPTR_WR_ENA);
3731 ring->wptr = 0;
3732 WREG32(CP_RB1_WPTR, ring->wptr);
3733
3734 /* set the wb address whether it's enabled or not */
3735 WREG32(CP_RB1_RPTR_ADDR, (rdev->wb.gpu_addr + RADEON_WB_CP1_RPTR_OFFSET) & 0xFFFFFFFC);
3736 WREG32(CP_RB1_RPTR_ADDR_HI, upper_32_bits(rdev->wb.gpu_addr + RADEON_WB_CP1_RPTR_OFFSET) & 0xFF);
3737
3738 mdelay(1);
3739 WREG32(CP_RB1_CNTL, tmp);
3740
3741 WREG32(CP_RB1_BASE, ring->gpu_addr >> 8);
3742
3743 /* ring2 - compute only */
3744 /* Set ring buffer size */
3745 ring = &rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX];
3746 rb_bufsz = order_base_2(ring->ring_size / 8);
3747 tmp = (order_base_2(RADEON_GPU_PAGE_SIZE/8) << 8) | rb_bufsz;
3748#ifdef __BIG_ENDIAN
3749 tmp |= BUF_SWAP_32BIT;
3750#endif
3751 WREG32(CP_RB2_CNTL, tmp);
3752
3753 /* Initialize the ring buffer's read and write pointers */
3754 WREG32(CP_RB2_CNTL, tmp | RB_RPTR_WR_ENA);
3755 ring->wptr = 0;
3756 WREG32(CP_RB2_WPTR, ring->wptr);
3757
3758 /* set the wb address whether it's enabled or not */
3759 WREG32(CP_RB2_RPTR_ADDR, (rdev->wb.gpu_addr + RADEON_WB_CP2_RPTR_OFFSET) & 0xFFFFFFFC);
3760 WREG32(CP_RB2_RPTR_ADDR_HI, upper_32_bits(rdev->wb.gpu_addr + RADEON_WB_CP2_RPTR_OFFSET) & 0xFF);
3761
3762 mdelay(1);
3763 WREG32(CP_RB2_CNTL, tmp);
3764
3765 WREG32(CP_RB2_BASE, ring->gpu_addr >> 8);
3766
3767 /* start the rings */
3768 si_cp_start(rdev);
3769 rdev->ring[RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX].ready = true;
3770 rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX].ready = true;
3771 rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX].ready = true;
3772 r = radeon_ring_test(rdev, RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX, &rdev->ring[RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX]);
3773 if (r) {
3774 rdev->ring[RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX].ready = false;
3775 rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX].ready = false;
3776 rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX].ready = false;
3777 return r;
3778 }
3779 r = radeon_ring_test(rdev, CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX, &rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX]);
3780 if (r) {
3781 rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX].ready = false;
3782 }
3783 r = radeon_ring_test(rdev, CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX, &rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX]);
3784 if (r) {
3785 rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX].ready = false;
3786 }
3787
3788 si_enable_gui_idle_interrupt(rdev, true);
3789
3790 if (rdev->asic->copy.copy_ring_index == RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX)
3791 radeon_ttm_set_active_vram_size(rdev, rdev->mc.real_vram_size);
3792
3793 return 0;
3794}
3795
3796u32 si_gpu_check_soft_reset(struct radeon_device *rdev)
3797{
3798 u32 reset_mask = 0;
3799 u32 tmp;
3800
3801 /* GRBM_STATUS */
3802 tmp = RREG32(GRBM_STATUS);
3803 if (tmp & (PA_BUSY | SC_BUSY |
3804 BCI_BUSY | SX_BUSY |
3805 TA_BUSY | VGT_BUSY |
3806 DB_BUSY | CB_BUSY |
3807 GDS_BUSY | SPI_BUSY |
3808 IA_BUSY | IA_BUSY_NO_DMA))
3809 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_GFX;
3810
3811 if (tmp & (CF_RQ_PENDING | PF_RQ_PENDING |
3812 CP_BUSY | CP_COHERENCY_BUSY))
3813 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_CP;
3814
3815 if (tmp & GRBM_EE_BUSY)
3816 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_GRBM | RADEON_RESET_GFX | RADEON_RESET_CP;
3817
3818 /* GRBM_STATUS2 */
3819 tmp = RREG32(GRBM_STATUS2);
3820 if (tmp & (RLC_RQ_PENDING | RLC_BUSY))
3821 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_RLC;
3822
3823 /* DMA_STATUS_REG 0 */
3824 tmp = RREG32(DMA_STATUS_REG + DMA0_REGISTER_OFFSET);
3825 if (!(tmp & DMA_IDLE))
3826 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_DMA;
3827
3828 /* DMA_STATUS_REG 1 */
3829 tmp = RREG32(DMA_STATUS_REG + DMA1_REGISTER_OFFSET);
3830 if (!(tmp & DMA_IDLE))
3831 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_DMA1;
3832
3833 /* SRBM_STATUS2 */
3834 tmp = RREG32(SRBM_STATUS2);
3835 if (tmp & DMA_BUSY)
3836 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_DMA;
3837
3838 if (tmp & DMA1_BUSY)
3839 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_DMA1;
3840
3841 /* SRBM_STATUS */
3842 tmp = RREG32(SRBM_STATUS);
3843
3844 if (tmp & IH_BUSY)
3845 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_IH;
3846
3847 if (tmp & SEM_BUSY)
3848 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_SEM;
3849
3850 if (tmp & GRBM_RQ_PENDING)
3851 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_GRBM;
3852
3853 if (tmp & VMC_BUSY)
3854 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_VMC;
3855
3856 if (tmp & (MCB_BUSY | MCB_NON_DISPLAY_BUSY |
3857 MCC_BUSY | MCD_BUSY))
3858 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_MC;
3859
3860 if (evergreen_is_display_hung(rdev))
3861 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_DISPLAY;
3862
3863 /* VM_L2_STATUS */
3864 tmp = RREG32(VM_L2_STATUS);
3865 if (tmp & L2_BUSY)
3866 reset_mask |= RADEON_RESET_VMC;
3867
3868 /* Skip MC reset as it's mostly likely not hung, just busy */
3869 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_MC) {
3870 DRM_DEBUG("MC busy: 0x%08X, clearing.\n", reset_mask);
3871 reset_mask &= ~RADEON_RESET_MC;
3872 }
3873
3874 return reset_mask;
3875}
3876
3877static void si_gpu_soft_reset(struct radeon_device *rdev, u32 reset_mask)
3878{
3879 struct evergreen_mc_save save;
3880 u32 grbm_soft_reset = 0, srbm_soft_reset = 0;
3881 u32 tmp;
3882
3883 if (reset_mask == 0)
3884 return;
3885
3886 dev_info(rdev->dev, "GPU softreset: 0x%08X\n", reset_mask);
3887
3888 evergreen_print_gpu_status_regs(rdev);
3889 dev_info(rdev->dev, " VM_CONTEXT1_PROTECTION_FAULT_ADDR 0x%08X\n",
3890 RREG32(VM_CONTEXT1_PROTECTION_FAULT_ADDR));
3891 dev_info(rdev->dev, " VM_CONTEXT1_PROTECTION_FAULT_STATUS 0x%08X\n",
3892 RREG32(VM_CONTEXT1_PROTECTION_FAULT_STATUS));
3893
3894 /* disable PG/CG */
3895 si_fini_pg(rdev);
3896 si_fini_cg(rdev);
3897
3898 /* stop the rlc */
3899 si_rlc_stop(rdev);
3900
3901 /* Disable CP parsing/prefetching */
3902 WREG32(CP_ME_CNTL, CP_ME_HALT | CP_PFP_HALT | CP_CE_HALT);
3903
3904 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_DMA) {
3905 /* dma0 */
3906 tmp = RREG32(DMA_RB_CNTL + DMA0_REGISTER_OFFSET);
3907 tmp &= ~DMA_RB_ENABLE;
3908 WREG32(DMA_RB_CNTL + DMA0_REGISTER_OFFSET, tmp);
3909 }
3910 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_DMA1) {
3911 /* dma1 */
3912 tmp = RREG32(DMA_RB_CNTL + DMA1_REGISTER_OFFSET);
3913 tmp &= ~DMA_RB_ENABLE;
3914 WREG32(DMA_RB_CNTL + DMA1_REGISTER_OFFSET, tmp);
3915 }
3916
3917 udelay(50);
3918
3919 evergreen_mc_stop(rdev, &save);
3920 if (evergreen_mc_wait_for_idle(rdev)) {
3921 dev_warn(rdev->dev, "Wait for MC idle timedout !\n");
3922 }
3923
3924 if (reset_mask & (RADEON_RESET_GFX | RADEON_RESET_COMPUTE | RADEON_RESET_CP)) {
3925 grbm_soft_reset = SOFT_RESET_CB |
3926 SOFT_RESET_DB |
3927 SOFT_RESET_GDS |
3928 SOFT_RESET_PA |
3929 SOFT_RESET_SC |
3930 SOFT_RESET_BCI |
3931 SOFT_RESET_SPI |
3932 SOFT_RESET_SX |
3933 SOFT_RESET_TC |
3934 SOFT_RESET_TA |
3935 SOFT_RESET_VGT |
3936 SOFT_RESET_IA;
3937 }
3938
3939 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_CP) {
3940 grbm_soft_reset |= SOFT_RESET_CP | SOFT_RESET_VGT;
3941
3942 srbm_soft_reset |= SOFT_RESET_GRBM;
3943 }
3944
3945 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_DMA)
3946 srbm_soft_reset |= SOFT_RESET_DMA;
3947
3948 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_DMA1)
3949 srbm_soft_reset |= SOFT_RESET_DMA1;
3950
3951 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_DISPLAY)
3952 srbm_soft_reset |= SOFT_RESET_DC;
3953
3954 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_RLC)
3955 grbm_soft_reset |= SOFT_RESET_RLC;
3956
3957 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_SEM)
3958 srbm_soft_reset |= SOFT_RESET_SEM;
3959
3960 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_IH)
3961 srbm_soft_reset |= SOFT_RESET_IH;
3962
3963 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_GRBM)
3964 srbm_soft_reset |= SOFT_RESET_GRBM;
3965
3966 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_VMC)
3967 srbm_soft_reset |= SOFT_RESET_VMC;
3968
3969 if (reset_mask & RADEON_RESET_MC)
3970 srbm_soft_reset |= SOFT_RESET_MC;
3971
3972 if (grbm_soft_reset) {
3973 tmp = RREG32(GRBM_SOFT_RESET);
3974 tmp |= grbm_soft_reset;
3975 dev_info(rdev->dev, "GRBM_SOFT_RESET=0x%08X\n", tmp);
3976 WREG32(GRBM_SOFT_RESET, tmp);
3977 tmp = RREG32(GRBM_SOFT_RESET);
3978
3979 udelay(50);
3980
3981 tmp &= ~grbm_soft_reset;
3982 WREG32(GRBM_SOFT_RESET, tmp);
3983 tmp = RREG32(GRBM_SOFT_RESET);
3984 }
3985
3986 if (srbm_soft_reset) {
3987 tmp = RREG32(SRBM_SOFT_RESET);
3988 tmp |= srbm_soft_reset;
3989 dev_info(rdev->dev, "SRBM_SOFT_RESET=0x%08X\n", tmp);
3990 WREG32(SRBM_SOFT_RESET, tmp);
3991 tmp = RREG32(SRBM_SOFT_RESET);
3992
3993 udelay(50);
3994
3995 tmp &= ~srbm_soft_reset;
3996 WREG32(SRBM_SOFT_RESET, tmp);
3997 tmp = RREG32(SRBM_SOFT_RESET);
3998 }
3999
4000 /* Wait a little for things to settle down */
4001 udelay(50);
4002
4003 evergreen_mc_resume(rdev, &save);
4004 udelay(50);
4005
4006 evergreen_print_gpu_status_regs(rdev);
4007}
4008
4009static void si_set_clk_bypass_mode(struct radeon_device *rdev)
4010{
4011 u32 tmp, i;
4012
4013 tmp = RREG32(CG_SPLL_FUNC_CNTL);
4014 tmp |= SPLL_BYPASS_EN;
4015 WREG32(CG_SPLL_FUNC_CNTL, tmp);
4016
4017 tmp = RREG32(CG_SPLL_FUNC_CNTL_2);
4018 tmp |= SPLL_CTLREQ_CHG;
4019 WREG32(CG_SPLL_FUNC_CNTL_2, tmp);
4020
4021 for (i = 0; i < rdev->usec_timeout; i++) {
4022 if (RREG32(SPLL_STATUS) & SPLL_CHG_STATUS)
4023 break;
4024 udelay(1);
4025 }
4026
4027 tmp = RREG32(CG_SPLL_FUNC_CNTL_2);
4028 tmp &= ~(SPLL_CTLREQ_CHG | SCLK_MUX_UPDATE);
4029 WREG32(CG_SPLL_FUNC_CNTL_2, tmp);
4030
4031 tmp = RREG32(MPLL_CNTL_MODE);
4032 tmp &= ~MPLL_MCLK_SEL;
4033 WREG32(MPLL_CNTL_MODE, tmp);
4034}
4035
4036static void si_spll_powerdown(struct radeon_device *rdev)
4037{
4038 u32 tmp;
4039
4040 tmp = RREG32(SPLL_CNTL_MODE);
4041 tmp |= SPLL_SW_DIR_CONTROL;
4042 WREG32(SPLL_CNTL_MODE, tmp);
4043
4044 tmp = RREG32(CG_SPLL_FUNC_CNTL);
4045 tmp |= SPLL_RESET;
4046 WREG32(CG_SPLL_FUNC_CNTL, tmp);
4047
4048 tmp = RREG32(CG_SPLL_FUNC_CNTL);
4049 tmp |= SPLL_SLEEP;
4050 WREG32(CG_SPLL_FUNC_CNTL, tmp);
4051
4052 tmp = RREG32(SPLL_CNTL_MODE);
4053 tmp &= ~SPLL_SW_DIR_CONTROL;
4054 WREG32(SPLL_CNTL_MODE, tmp);
4055}
4056
4057static void si_gpu_pci_config_reset(struct radeon_device *rdev)
4058{
4059 struct evergreen_mc_save save;
4060 u32 tmp, i;
4061
4062 dev_info(rdev->dev, "GPU pci config reset\n");
4063
4064 /* disable dpm? */
4065
4066 /* disable cg/pg */
4067 si_fini_pg(rdev);
4068 si_fini_cg(rdev);
4069
4070 /* Disable CP parsing/prefetching */
4071 WREG32(CP_ME_CNTL, CP_ME_HALT | CP_PFP_HALT | CP_CE_HALT);
4072 /* dma0 */
4073 tmp = RREG32(DMA_RB_CNTL + DMA0_REGISTER_OFFSET);
4074 tmp &= ~DMA_RB_ENABLE;
4075 WREG32(DMA_RB_CNTL + DMA0_REGISTER_OFFSET, tmp);
4076 /* dma1 */
4077 tmp = RREG32(DMA_RB_CNTL + DMA1_REGISTER_OFFSET);
4078 tmp &= ~DMA_RB_ENABLE;
4079 WREG32(DMA_RB_CNTL + DMA1_REGISTER_OFFSET, tmp);
4080 /* XXX other engines? */
4081
4082 /* halt the rlc, disable cp internal ints */
4083 si_rlc_stop(rdev);
4084
4085 udelay(50);
4086
4087 /* disable mem access */
4088 evergreen_mc_stop(rdev, &save);
4089 if (evergreen_mc_wait_for_idle(rdev)) {
4090 dev_warn(rdev->dev, "Wait for MC idle timed out !\n");
4091 }
4092
4093 /* set mclk/sclk to bypass */
4094 si_set_clk_bypass_mode(rdev);
4095 /* powerdown spll */
4096 si_spll_powerdown(rdev);
4097 /* disable BM */
4098 pci_clear_master(rdev->pdev);
4099 /* reset */
4100 radeon_pci_config_reset(rdev);
4101 /* wait for asic to come out of reset */
4102 for (i = 0; i < rdev->usec_timeout; i++) {
4103 if (RREG32(CONFIG_MEMSIZE) != 0xffffffff)
4104 break;
4105 udelay(1);
4106 }
4107}
4108
4109int si_asic_reset(struct radeon_device *rdev)
4110{
4111 u32 reset_mask;
4112
4113 reset_mask = si_gpu_check_soft_reset(rdev);
4114
4115 if (reset_mask)
4116 r600_set_bios_scratch_engine_hung(rdev, true);
4117
4118 /* try soft reset */
4119 si_gpu_soft_reset(rdev, reset_mask);
4120
4121 reset_mask = si_gpu_check_soft_reset(rdev);
4122
4123 /* try pci config reset */
4124 if (reset_mask && radeon_hard_reset)
4125 si_gpu_pci_config_reset(rdev);
4126
4127 reset_mask = si_gpu_check_soft_reset(rdev);
4128
4129 if (!reset_mask)
4130 r600_set_bios_scratch_engine_hung(rdev, false);
4131
4132 return 0;
4133}
4134
4135/**
4136 * si_gfx_is_lockup - Check if the GFX engine is locked up
4137 *
4138 * @rdev: radeon_device pointer
4139 * @ring: radeon_ring structure holding ring information
4140 *
4141 * Check if the GFX engine is locked up.
4142 * Returns true if the engine appears to be locked up, false if not.
4143 */
4144bool si_gfx_is_lockup(struct radeon_device *rdev, struct radeon_ring *ring)
4145{
4146 u32 reset_mask = si_gpu_check_soft_reset(rdev);
4147
4148 if (!(reset_mask & (RADEON_RESET_GFX |
4149 RADEON_RESET_COMPUTE |
4150 RADEON_RESET_CP))) {
4151 radeon_ring_lockup_update(rdev, ring);
4152 return false;
4153 }
4154 return radeon_ring_test_lockup(rdev, ring);
4155}
4156
4157/* MC */
4158static void si_mc_program(struct radeon_device *rdev)
4159{
4160 struct evergreen_mc_save save;
4161 u32 tmp;
4162 int i, j;
4163
4164 /* Initialize HDP */
4165 for (i = 0, j = 0; i < 32; i++, j += 0x18) {
4166 WREG32((0x2c14 + j), 0x00000000);
4167 WREG32((0x2c18 + j), 0x00000000);
4168 WREG32((0x2c1c + j), 0x00000000);
4169 WREG32((0x2c20 + j), 0x00000000);
4170 WREG32((0x2c24 + j), 0x00000000);
4171 }
4172 WREG32(HDP_REG_COHERENCY_FLUSH_CNTL, 0);
4173
4174 evergreen_mc_stop(rdev, &save);
4175 if (radeon_mc_wait_for_idle(rdev)) {
4176 dev_warn(rdev->dev, "Wait for MC idle timedout !\n");
4177 }
4178 if (!ASIC_IS_NODCE(rdev))
4179 /* Lockout access through VGA aperture*/
4180 WREG32(VGA_HDP_CONTROL, VGA_MEMORY_DISABLE);
4181 /* Update configuration */
4182 WREG32(MC_VM_SYSTEM_APERTURE_LOW_ADDR,
4183 rdev->mc.vram_start >> 12);
4184 WREG32(MC_VM_SYSTEM_APERTURE_HIGH_ADDR,
4185 rdev->mc.vram_end >> 12);
4186 WREG32(MC_VM_SYSTEM_APERTURE_DEFAULT_ADDR,
4187 rdev->vram_scratch.gpu_addr >> 12);
4188 tmp = ((rdev->mc.vram_end >> 24) & 0xFFFF) << 16;
4189 tmp |= ((rdev->mc.vram_start >> 24) & 0xFFFF);
4190 WREG32(MC_VM_FB_LOCATION, tmp);
4191 /* XXX double check these! */
4192 WREG32(HDP_NONSURFACE_BASE, (rdev->mc.vram_start >> 8));
4193 WREG32(HDP_NONSURFACE_INFO, (2 << 7) | (1 << 30));
4194 WREG32(HDP_NONSURFACE_SIZE, 0x3FFFFFFF);
4195 WREG32(MC_VM_AGP_BASE, 0);
4196 WREG32(MC_VM_AGP_TOP, 0x0FFFFFFF);
4197 WREG32(MC_VM_AGP_BOT, 0x0FFFFFFF);
4198 if (radeon_mc_wait_for_idle(rdev)) {
4199 dev_warn(rdev->dev, "Wait for MC idle timedout !\n");
4200 }
4201 evergreen_mc_resume(rdev, &save);
4202 if (!ASIC_IS_NODCE(rdev)) {
4203 /* we need to own VRAM, so turn off the VGA renderer here
4204 * to stop it overwriting our objects */
4205 rv515_vga_render_disable(rdev);
4206 }
4207}
4208
4209void si_vram_gtt_location(struct radeon_device *rdev,
4210 struct radeon_mc *mc)
4211{
4212 if (mc->mc_vram_size > 0xFFC0000000ULL) {
4213 /* leave room for at least 1024M GTT */
4214 dev_warn(rdev->dev, "limiting VRAM\n");
4215 mc->real_vram_size = 0xFFC0000000ULL;
4216 mc->mc_vram_size = 0xFFC0000000ULL;
4217 }
4218 radeon_vram_location(rdev, &rdev->mc, 0);
4219 rdev->mc.gtt_base_align = 0;
4220 radeon_gtt_location(rdev, mc);
4221}
4222
4223static int si_mc_init(struct radeon_device *rdev)
4224{
4225 u32 tmp;
4226 int chansize, numchan;
4227
4228 /* Get VRAM informations */
4229 rdev->mc.vram_is_ddr = true;
4230 tmp = RREG32(MC_ARB_RAMCFG);
4231 if (tmp & CHANSIZE_OVERRIDE) {
4232 chansize = 16;
4233 } else if (tmp & CHANSIZE_MASK) {
4234 chansize = 64;
4235 } else {
4236 chansize = 32;
4237 }
4238 tmp = RREG32(MC_SHARED_CHMAP);
4239 switch ((tmp & NOOFCHAN_MASK) >> NOOFCHAN_SHIFT) {
4240 case 0:
4241 default:
4242 numchan = 1;
4243 break;
4244 case 1:
4245 numchan = 2;
4246 break;
4247 case 2:
4248 numchan = 4;
4249 break;
4250 case 3:
4251 numchan = 8;
4252 break;
4253 case 4:
4254 numchan = 3;
4255 break;
4256 case 5:
4257 numchan = 6;
4258 break;
4259 case 6:
4260 numchan = 10;
4261 break;
4262 case 7:
4263 numchan = 12;
4264 break;
4265 case 8:
4266 numchan = 16;
4267 break;
4268 }
4269 rdev->mc.vram_width = numchan * chansize;
4270 /* Could aper size report 0 ? */
4271 rdev->mc.aper_base = pci_resource_start(rdev->pdev, 0);
4272 rdev->mc.aper_size = pci_resource_len(rdev->pdev, 0);
4273 /* size in MB on si */
4274 tmp = RREG32(CONFIG_MEMSIZE);
4275 /* some boards may have garbage in the upper 16 bits */
4276 if (tmp & 0xffff0000) {
4277 DRM_INFO("Probable bad vram size: 0x%08x\n", tmp);
4278 if (tmp & 0xffff)
4279 tmp &= 0xffff;
4280 }
4281 rdev->mc.mc_vram_size = tmp * 1024ULL * 1024ULL;
4282 rdev->mc.real_vram_size = rdev->mc.mc_vram_size;
4283 rdev->mc.visible_vram_size = rdev->mc.aper_size;
4284 si_vram_gtt_location(rdev, &rdev->mc);
4285 radeon_update_bandwidth_info(rdev);
4286
4287 return 0;
4288}
4289
4290/*
4291 * GART
4292 */
4293void si_pcie_gart_tlb_flush(struct radeon_device *rdev)
4294{
4295 /* flush hdp cache */
4296 WREG32(HDP_MEM_COHERENCY_FLUSH_CNTL, 0x1);
4297
4298 /* bits 0-15 are the VM contexts0-15 */
4299 WREG32(VM_INVALIDATE_REQUEST, 1);
4300}
4301
4302static int si_pcie_gart_enable(struct radeon_device *rdev)
4303{
4304 int r, i;
4305
4306 if (rdev->gart.robj == NULL) {
4307 dev_err(rdev->dev, "No VRAM object for PCIE GART.\n");
4308 return -EINVAL;
4309 }
4310 r = radeon_gart_table_vram_pin(rdev);
4311 if (r)
4312 return r;
4313 /* Setup TLB control */
4314 WREG32(MC_VM_MX_L1_TLB_CNTL,
4315 (0xA << 7) |
4316 ENABLE_L1_TLB |
4317 ENABLE_L1_FRAGMENT_PROCESSING |
4318 SYSTEM_ACCESS_MODE_NOT_IN_SYS |
4319 ENABLE_ADVANCED_DRIVER_MODEL |
4320 SYSTEM_APERTURE_UNMAPPED_ACCESS_PASS_THRU);
4321 /* Setup L2 cache */
4322 WREG32(VM_L2_CNTL, ENABLE_L2_CACHE |
4323 ENABLE_L2_FRAGMENT_PROCESSING |
4324 ENABLE_L2_PTE_CACHE_LRU_UPDATE_BY_WRITE |
4325 ENABLE_L2_PDE0_CACHE_LRU_UPDATE_BY_WRITE |
4326 EFFECTIVE_L2_QUEUE_SIZE(7) |
4327 CONTEXT1_IDENTITY_ACCESS_MODE(1));
4328 WREG32(VM_L2_CNTL2, INVALIDATE_ALL_L1_TLBS | INVALIDATE_L2_CACHE);
4329 WREG32(VM_L2_CNTL3, L2_CACHE_BIGK_ASSOCIATIVITY |
4330 BANK_SELECT(4) |
4331 L2_CACHE_BIGK_FRAGMENT_SIZE(4));
4332 /* setup context0 */
4333 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT0_PAGE_TABLE_START_ADDR, rdev->mc.gtt_start >> 12);
4334 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT0_PAGE_TABLE_END_ADDR, rdev->mc.gtt_end >> 12);
4335 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT0_PAGE_TABLE_BASE_ADDR, rdev->gart.table_addr >> 12);
4336 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT0_PROTECTION_FAULT_DEFAULT_ADDR,
4337 (u32)(rdev->dummy_page.addr >> 12));
4338 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT0_CNTL2, 0);
4339 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT0_CNTL, (ENABLE_CONTEXT | PAGE_TABLE_DEPTH(0) |
4340 RANGE_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_DEFAULT));
4341
4342 WREG32(0x15D4, 0);
4343 WREG32(0x15D8, 0);
4344 WREG32(0x15DC, 0);
4345
4346 /* empty context1-15 */
4347 /* set vm size, must be a multiple of 4 */
4348 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT1_PAGE_TABLE_START_ADDR, 0);
4349 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT1_PAGE_TABLE_END_ADDR, rdev->vm_manager.max_pfn - 1);
4350 /* Assign the pt base to something valid for now; the pts used for
4351 * the VMs are determined by the application and setup and assigned
4352 * on the fly in the vm part of radeon_gart.c
4353 */
4354 for (i = 1; i < 16; i++) {
4355 if (i < 8)
4356 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT0_PAGE_TABLE_BASE_ADDR + (i << 2),
4357 rdev->vm_manager.saved_table_addr[i]);
4358 else
4359 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT8_PAGE_TABLE_BASE_ADDR + ((i - 8) << 2),
4360 rdev->vm_manager.saved_table_addr[i]);
4361 }
4362
4363 /* enable context1-15 */
4364 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT1_PROTECTION_FAULT_DEFAULT_ADDR,
4365 (u32)(rdev->dummy_page.addr >> 12));
4366 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT1_CNTL2, 4);
4367 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT1_CNTL, ENABLE_CONTEXT | PAGE_TABLE_DEPTH(1) |
4368 PAGE_TABLE_BLOCK_SIZE(radeon_vm_block_size - 9) |
4369 RANGE_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_INTERRUPT |
4370 RANGE_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_DEFAULT |
4371 DUMMY_PAGE_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_INTERRUPT |
4372 DUMMY_PAGE_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_DEFAULT |
4373 PDE0_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_INTERRUPT |
4374 PDE0_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_DEFAULT |
4375 VALID_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_INTERRUPT |
4376 VALID_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_DEFAULT |
4377 READ_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_INTERRUPT |
4378 READ_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_DEFAULT |
4379 WRITE_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_INTERRUPT |
4380 WRITE_PROTECTION_FAULT_ENABLE_DEFAULT);
4381
4382 si_pcie_gart_tlb_flush(rdev);
4383 DRM_INFO("PCIE GART of %uM enabled (table at 0x%016llX).\n",
4384 (unsigned)(rdev->mc.gtt_size >> 20),
4385 (unsigned long long)rdev->gart.table_addr);
4386 rdev->gart.ready = true;
4387 return 0;
4388}
4389
4390static void si_pcie_gart_disable(struct radeon_device *rdev)
4391{
4392 unsigned i;
4393
4394 for (i = 1; i < 16; ++i) {
4395 uint32_t reg;
4396 if (i < 8)
4397 reg = VM_CONTEXT0_PAGE_TABLE_BASE_ADDR + (i << 2);
4398 else
4399 reg = VM_CONTEXT8_PAGE_TABLE_BASE_ADDR + ((i - 8) << 2);
4400 rdev->vm_manager.saved_table_addr[i] = RREG32(reg);
4401 }
4402
4403 /* Disable all tables */
4404 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT0_CNTL, 0);
4405 WREG32(VM_CONTEXT1_CNTL, 0);
4406 /* Setup TLB control */
4407 WREG32(MC_VM_MX_L1_TLB_CNTL, SYSTEM_ACCESS_MODE_NOT_IN_SYS |
4408 SYSTEM_APERTURE_UNMAPPED_ACCESS_PASS_THRU);
4409 /* Setup L2 cache */
4410 WREG32(VM_L2_CNTL, ENABLE_L2_PTE_CACHE_LRU_UPDATE_BY_WRITE |
4411 ENABLE_L2_PDE0_CACHE_LRU_UPDATE_BY_WRITE |
4412 EFFECTIVE_L2_QUEUE_SIZE(7) |
4413 CONTEXT1_IDENTITY_ACCESS_MODE(1));
4414 WREG32(VM_L2_CNTL2, 0);
4415 WREG32(VM_L2_CNTL3, L2_CACHE_BIGK_ASSOCIATIVITY |
4416 L2_CACHE_BIGK_FRAGMENT_SIZE(0));
4417 radeon_gart_table_vram_unpin(rdev);
4418}
4419
4420static void si_pcie_gart_fini(struct radeon_device *rdev)
4421{
4422 si_pcie_gart_disable(rdev);
4423 radeon_gart_table_vram_free(rdev);
4424 radeon_gart_fini(rdev);
4425}
4426
4427/* vm parser */
4428static bool si_vm_reg_valid(u32 reg)
4429{
4430 /* context regs are fine */
4431 if (reg >= 0x28000)
4432 return true;
4433
4434 /* check config regs */
4435 switch (reg) {
4436 case GRBM_GFX_INDEX:
4437 case CP_STRMOUT_CNTL:
4438 case VGT_VTX_VECT_EJECT_REG:
4439 case VGT_CACHE_INVALIDATION:
4440 case VGT_ESGS_RING_SIZE:
4441 case VGT_GSVS_RING_SIZE:
4442 case VGT_GS_VERTEX_REUSE:
4443 case VGT_PRIMITIVE_TYPE:
4444 case VGT_INDEX_TYPE:
4445 case VGT_NUM_INDICES:
4446 case VGT_NUM_INSTANCES:
4447 case VGT_TF_RING_SIZE:
4448 case VGT_HS_OFFCHIP_PARAM:
4449 case VGT_TF_MEMORY_BASE:
4450 case PA_CL_ENHANCE:
4451 case PA_SU_LINE_STIPPLE_VALUE:
4452 case PA_SC_LINE_STIPPLE_STATE:
4453 case PA_SC_ENHANCE:
4454 case SQC_CACHES:
4455 case SPI_STATIC_THREAD_MGMT_1:
4456 case SPI_STATIC_THREAD_MGMT_2:
4457 case SPI_STATIC_THREAD_MGMT_3:
4458 case SPI_PS_MAX_WAVE_ID:
4459 case SPI_CONFIG_CNTL:
4460 case SPI_CONFIG_CNTL_1:
4461 case TA_CNTL_AUX:
4462 return true;
4463 default:
4464 DRM_ERROR("Invalid register 0x%x in CS\n", reg);
4465 return false;
4466 }
4467}
4468
4469static int si_vm_packet3_ce_check(struct radeon_device *rdev,
4470 u32 *ib, struct radeon_cs_packet *pkt)
4471{
4472 switch (pkt->opcode) {
4473 case PACKET3_NOP:
4474 case PACKET3_SET_BASE:
4475 case PACKET3_SET_CE_DE_COUNTERS:
4476 case PACKET3_LOAD_CONST_RAM:
4477 case PACKET3_WRITE_CONST_RAM:
4478 case PACKET3_WRITE_CONST_RAM_OFFSET:
4479 case PACKET3_DUMP_CONST_RAM:
4480 case PACKET3_INCREMENT_CE_COUNTER:
4481 case PACKET3_WAIT_ON_DE_COUNTER:
4482 case PACKET3_CE_WRITE:
4483 break;
4484 default:
4485 DRM_ERROR("Invalid CE packet3: 0x%x\n", pkt->opcode);
4486 return -EINVAL;
4487 }
4488 return 0;
4489}
4490
4491static int si_vm_packet3_cp_dma_check(u32 *ib, u32 idx)
4492{
4493 u32 start_reg, reg, i;
4494 u32 command = ib[idx + 4];
4495 u32 info = ib[idx + 1];
4496 u32 idx_value = ib[idx];
4497 if (command & PACKET3_CP_DMA_CMD_SAS) {
4498 /* src address space is register */
4499 if (((info & 0x60000000) >> 29) == 0) {
4500 start_reg = idx_value << 2;
4501 if (command & PACKET3_CP_DMA_CMD_SAIC) {
4502 reg = start_reg;
4503 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg)) {
4504 DRM_ERROR("CP DMA Bad SRC register\n");
4505 return -EINVAL;
4506 }
4507 } else {
4508 for (i = 0; i < (command & 0x1fffff); i++) {
4509 reg = start_reg + (4 * i);
4510 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg)) {
4511 DRM_ERROR("CP DMA Bad SRC register\n");
4512 return -EINVAL;
4513 }
4514 }
4515 }
4516 }
4517 }
4518 if (command & PACKET3_CP_DMA_CMD_DAS) {
4519 /* dst address space is register */
4520 if (((info & 0x00300000) >> 20) == 0) {
4521 start_reg = ib[idx + 2];
4522 if (command & PACKET3_CP_DMA_CMD_DAIC) {
4523 reg = start_reg;
4524 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg)) {
4525 DRM_ERROR("CP DMA Bad DST register\n");
4526 return -EINVAL;
4527 }
4528 } else {
4529 for (i = 0; i < (command & 0x1fffff); i++) {
4530 reg = start_reg + (4 * i);
4531 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg)) {
4532 DRM_ERROR("CP DMA Bad DST register\n");
4533 return -EINVAL;
4534 }
4535 }
4536 }
4537 }
4538 }
4539 return 0;
4540}
4541
4542static int si_vm_packet3_gfx_check(struct radeon_device *rdev,
4543 u32 *ib, struct radeon_cs_packet *pkt)
4544{
4545 int r;
4546 u32 idx = pkt->idx + 1;
4547 u32 idx_value = ib[idx];
4548 u32 start_reg, end_reg, reg, i;
4549
4550 switch (pkt->opcode) {
4551 case PACKET3_NOP:
4552 case PACKET3_SET_BASE:
4553 case PACKET3_CLEAR_STATE:
4554 case PACKET3_INDEX_BUFFER_SIZE:
4555 case PACKET3_DISPATCH_DIRECT:
4556 case PACKET3_DISPATCH_INDIRECT:
4557 case PACKET3_ALLOC_GDS:
4558 case PACKET3_WRITE_GDS_RAM:
4559 case PACKET3_ATOMIC_GDS:
4560 case PACKET3_ATOMIC:
4561 case PACKET3_OCCLUSION_QUERY:
4562 case PACKET3_SET_PREDICATION:
4563 case PACKET3_COND_EXEC:
4564 case PACKET3_PRED_EXEC:
4565 case PACKET3_DRAW_INDIRECT:
4566 case PACKET3_DRAW_INDEX_INDIRECT:
4567 case PACKET3_INDEX_BASE:
4568 case PACKET3_DRAW_INDEX_2:
4569 case PACKET3_CONTEXT_CONTROL:
4570 case PACKET3_INDEX_TYPE:
4571 case PACKET3_DRAW_INDIRECT_MULTI:
4572 case PACKET3_DRAW_INDEX_AUTO:
4573 case PACKET3_DRAW_INDEX_IMMD:
4574 case PACKET3_NUM_INSTANCES:
4575 case PACKET3_DRAW_INDEX_MULTI_AUTO:
4576 case PACKET3_STRMOUT_BUFFER_UPDATE:
4577 case PACKET3_DRAW_INDEX_OFFSET_2:
4578 case PACKET3_DRAW_INDEX_MULTI_ELEMENT:
4579 case PACKET3_DRAW_INDEX_INDIRECT_MULTI:
4580 case PACKET3_MPEG_INDEX:
4581 case PACKET3_WAIT_REG_MEM:
4582 case PACKET3_MEM_WRITE:
4583 case PACKET3_PFP_SYNC_ME:
4584 case PACKET3_SURFACE_SYNC:
4585 case PACKET3_EVENT_WRITE:
4586 case PACKET3_EVENT_WRITE_EOP:
4587 case PACKET3_EVENT_WRITE_EOS:
4588 case PACKET3_SET_CONTEXT_REG:
4589 case PACKET3_SET_CONTEXT_REG_INDIRECT:
4590 case PACKET3_SET_SH_REG:
4591 case PACKET3_SET_SH_REG_OFFSET:
4592 case PACKET3_INCREMENT_DE_COUNTER:
4593 case PACKET3_WAIT_ON_CE_COUNTER:
4594 case PACKET3_WAIT_ON_AVAIL_BUFFER:
4595 case PACKET3_ME_WRITE:
4596 break;
4597 case PACKET3_COPY_DATA:
4598 if ((idx_value & 0xf00) == 0) {
4599 reg = ib[idx + 3] * 4;
4600 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg))
4601 return -EINVAL;
4602 }
4603 break;
4604 case PACKET3_WRITE_DATA:
4605 if ((idx_value & 0xf00) == 0) {
4606 start_reg = ib[idx + 1] * 4;
4607 if (idx_value & 0x10000) {
4608 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(start_reg))
4609 return -EINVAL;
4610 } else {
4611 for (i = 0; i < (pkt->count - 2); i++) {
4612 reg = start_reg + (4 * i);
4613 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg))
4614 return -EINVAL;
4615 }
4616 }
4617 }
4618 break;
4619 case PACKET3_COND_WRITE:
4620 if (idx_value & 0x100) {
4621 reg = ib[idx + 5] * 4;
4622 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg))
4623 return -EINVAL;
4624 }
4625 break;
4626 case PACKET3_COPY_DW:
4627 if (idx_value & 0x2) {
4628 reg = ib[idx + 3] * 4;
4629 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg))
4630 return -EINVAL;
4631 }
4632 break;
4633 case PACKET3_SET_CONFIG_REG:
4634 start_reg = (idx_value << 2) + PACKET3_SET_CONFIG_REG_START;
4635 end_reg = 4 * pkt->count + start_reg - 4;
4636 if ((start_reg < PACKET3_SET_CONFIG_REG_START) ||
4637 (start_reg >= PACKET3_SET_CONFIG_REG_END) ||
4638 (end_reg >= PACKET3_SET_CONFIG_REG_END)) {
4639 DRM_ERROR("bad PACKET3_SET_CONFIG_REG\n");
4640 return -EINVAL;
4641 }
4642 for (i = 0; i < pkt->count; i++) {
4643 reg = start_reg + (4 * i);
4644 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg))
4645 return -EINVAL;
4646 }
4647 break;
4648 case PACKET3_CP_DMA:
4649 r = si_vm_packet3_cp_dma_check(ib, idx);
4650 if (r)
4651 return r;
4652 break;
4653 default:
4654 DRM_ERROR("Invalid GFX packet3: 0x%x\n", pkt->opcode);
4655 return -EINVAL;
4656 }
4657 return 0;
4658}
4659
4660static int si_vm_packet3_compute_check(struct radeon_device *rdev,
4661 u32 *ib, struct radeon_cs_packet *pkt)
4662{
4663 int r;
4664 u32 idx = pkt->idx + 1;
4665 u32 idx_value = ib[idx];
4666 u32 start_reg, reg, i;
4667
4668 switch (pkt->opcode) {
4669 case PACKET3_NOP:
4670 case PACKET3_SET_BASE:
4671 case PACKET3_CLEAR_STATE:
4672 case PACKET3_DISPATCH_DIRECT:
4673 case PACKET3_DISPATCH_INDIRECT:
4674 case PACKET3_ALLOC_GDS:
4675 case PACKET3_WRITE_GDS_RAM:
4676 case PACKET3_ATOMIC_GDS:
4677 case PACKET3_ATOMIC:
4678 case PACKET3_OCCLUSION_QUERY:
4679 case PACKET3_SET_PREDICATION:
4680 case PACKET3_COND_EXEC:
4681 case PACKET3_PRED_EXEC:
4682 case PACKET3_CONTEXT_CONTROL:
4683 case PACKET3_STRMOUT_BUFFER_UPDATE:
4684 case PACKET3_WAIT_REG_MEM:
4685 case PACKET3_MEM_WRITE:
4686 case PACKET3_PFP_SYNC_ME:
4687 case PACKET3_SURFACE_SYNC:
4688 case PACKET3_EVENT_WRITE:
4689 case PACKET3_EVENT_WRITE_EOP:
4690 case PACKET3_EVENT_WRITE_EOS:
4691 case PACKET3_SET_CONTEXT_REG:
4692 case PACKET3_SET_CONTEXT_REG_INDIRECT:
4693 case PACKET3_SET_SH_REG:
4694 case PACKET3_SET_SH_REG_OFFSET:
4695 case PACKET3_INCREMENT_DE_COUNTER:
4696 case PACKET3_WAIT_ON_CE_COUNTER:
4697 case PACKET3_WAIT_ON_AVAIL_BUFFER:
4698 case PACKET3_ME_WRITE:
4699 break;
4700 case PACKET3_COPY_DATA:
4701 if ((idx_value & 0xf00) == 0) {
4702 reg = ib[idx + 3] * 4;
4703 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg))
4704 return -EINVAL;
4705 }
4706 break;
4707 case PACKET3_WRITE_DATA:
4708 if ((idx_value & 0xf00) == 0) {
4709 start_reg = ib[idx + 1] * 4;
4710 if (idx_value & 0x10000) {
4711 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(start_reg))
4712 return -EINVAL;
4713 } else {
4714 for (i = 0; i < (pkt->count - 2); i++) {
4715 reg = start_reg + (4 * i);
4716 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg))
4717 return -EINVAL;
4718 }
4719 }
4720 }
4721 break;
4722 case PACKET3_COND_WRITE:
4723 if (idx_value & 0x100) {
4724 reg = ib[idx + 5] * 4;
4725 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg))
4726 return -EINVAL;
4727 }
4728 break;
4729 case PACKET3_COPY_DW:
4730 if (idx_value & 0x2) {
4731 reg = ib[idx + 3] * 4;
4732 if (!si_vm_reg_valid(reg))
4733 return -EINVAL;
4734 }
4735 break;
4736 case PACKET3_CP_DMA:
4737 r = si_vm_packet3_cp_dma_check(ib, idx);
4738 if (r)
4739 return r;
4740 break;
4741 default:
4742 DRM_ERROR("Invalid Compute packet3: 0x%x\n", pkt->opcode);
4743 return -EINVAL;
4744 }
4745 return 0;
4746}
4747
4748int si_ib_parse(struct radeon_device *rdev, struct radeon_ib *ib)
4749{
4750 int ret = 0;
4751 u32 idx = 0, i;
4752 struct radeon_cs_packet pkt;
4753
4754 do {
4755 pkt.idx = idx;
4756 pkt.type = RADEON_CP_PACKET_GET_TYPE(ib->ptr[idx]);
4757 pkt.count = RADEON_CP_PACKET_GET_COUNT(ib->ptr[idx]);
4758 pkt.one_reg_wr = 0;
4759 switch (pkt.type) {
4760 case RADEON_PACKET_TYPE0:
4761 dev_err(rdev->dev, "Packet0 not allowed!\n");
4762 ret = -EINVAL;
4763 break;
4764 case RADEON_PACKET_TYPE2:
4765 idx += 1;
4766 break;
4767 case RADEON_PACKET_TYPE3:
4768 pkt.opcode = RADEON_CP_PACKET3_GET_OPCODE(ib->ptr[idx]);
4769 if (ib->is_const_ib)
4770 ret = si_vm_packet3_ce_check(rdev, ib->ptr, &pkt);
4771 else {
4772 switch (ib->ring) {
4773 case RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX:
4774 ret = si_vm_packet3_gfx_check(rdev, ib->ptr, &pkt);
4775 break;
4776 case CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX:
4777 case CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX:
4778 ret = si_vm_packet3_compute_check(rdev, ib->ptr, &pkt);
4779 break;
4780 default:
4781 dev_err(rdev->dev, "Non-PM4 ring %d !\n", ib->ring);
4782 ret = -EINVAL;
4783 break;
4784 }
4785 }
4786 idx += pkt.count + 2;
4787 break;
4788 default:
4789 dev_err(rdev->dev, "Unknown packet type %d !\n", pkt.type);
4790 ret = -EINVAL;
4791 break;
4792 }
4793 if (ret) {
4794 for (i = 0; i < ib->length_dw; i++) {
4795 if (i == idx)
4796 printk("\t0x%08x <---\n", ib->ptr[i]);
4797 else
4798 printk("\t0x%08x\n", ib->ptr[i]);
4799 }
4800 break;
4801 }
4802 } while (idx < ib->length_dw);
4803
4804 return ret;
4805}
4806
4807/*
4808 * vm
4809 */
4810int si_vm_init(struct radeon_device *rdev)
4811{
4812 /* number of VMs */
4813 rdev->vm_manager.nvm = 16;
4814 /* base offset of vram pages */
4815 rdev->vm_manager.vram_base_offset = 0;
4816
4817 return 0;
4818}

4822}

5087
5088void si_vm_flush(struct radeon_device *rdev, struct radeon_ring *ring,
5089 unsigned vm_id, uint64_t pd_addr)
5090{
5091 /* write new base address */
5092 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_WRITE_DATA, 3));
5093 radeon_ring_write(ring, (WRITE_DATA_ENGINE_SEL(1) |
5094 WRITE_DATA_DST_SEL(0)));
5095
5096 if (vm_id < 8) {
5097 radeon_ring_write(ring,
5098 (VM_CONTEXT0_PAGE_TABLE_BASE_ADDR + (vm_id << 2)) >> 2);
5099 } else {
5100 radeon_ring_write(ring,
5101 (VM_CONTEXT8_PAGE_TABLE_BASE_ADDR + ((vm_id - 8) << 2)) >> 2);
5102 }
5103 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
5104 radeon_ring_write(ring, pd_addr >> 12);
5105
5106 /* flush hdp cache */
5107 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_WRITE_DATA, 3));
5108 radeon_ring_write(ring, (WRITE_DATA_ENGINE_SEL(1) |
5109 WRITE_DATA_DST_SEL(0)));
5110 radeon_ring_write(ring, HDP_MEM_COHERENCY_FLUSH_CNTL >> 2);
5111 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
5112 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0x1);
5113
5114 /* bits 0-15 are the VM contexts0-15 */
5115 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_WRITE_DATA, 3));
5116 radeon_ring_write(ring, (WRITE_DATA_ENGINE_SEL(1) |
5117 WRITE_DATA_DST_SEL(0)));
5118 radeon_ring_write(ring, VM_INVALIDATE_REQUEST >> 2);
5119 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
5120 radeon_ring_write(ring, 1 << vm_id);
5121
5122 /* wait for the invalidate to complete */
5123 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_WAIT_REG_MEM, 5));
5124 radeon_ring_write(ring, (WAIT_REG_MEM_FUNCTION(0) | /* always */
5125 WAIT_REG_MEM_ENGINE(0))); /* me */
5126 radeon_ring_write(ring, VM_INVALIDATE_REQUEST >> 2);
5127 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0);
5128 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0); /* ref */
5129 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0); /* mask */
5130 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0x20); /* poll interval */
5131
5132 /* sync PFP to ME, otherwise we might get invalid PFP reads */
5133 radeon_ring_write(ring, PACKET3(PACKET3_PFP_SYNC_ME, 0));
5134 radeon_ring_write(ring, 0x0);
5135}
5136
5137/*
5138 * Power and clock gating
5139 */
5140static void si_wait_for_rlc_serdes(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5141{
5142 int i;
5143
5144 for (i = 0; i < rdev->usec_timeout; i++) {
5145 if (RREG32(RLC_SERDES_MASTER_BUSY_0) == 0)
5146 break;
5147 udelay(1);
5148 }
5149
5150 for (i = 0; i < rdev->usec_timeout; i++) {
5151 if (RREG32(RLC_SERDES_MASTER_BUSY_1) == 0)
5152 break;
5153 udelay(1);
5154 }
5155}
5156
5157static void si_enable_gui_idle_interrupt(struct radeon_device *rdev,
5158 bool enable)
5159{
5160 u32 tmp = RREG32(CP_INT_CNTL_RING0);
5161 u32 mask;
5162 int i;
5163
5164 if (enable)
5165 tmp |= (CNTX_BUSY_INT_ENABLE | CNTX_EMPTY_INT_ENABLE);
5166 else
5167 tmp &= ~(CNTX_BUSY_INT_ENABLE | CNTX_EMPTY_INT_ENABLE);
5168 WREG32(CP_INT_CNTL_RING0, tmp);
5169
5170 if (!enable) {
5171 /* read a gfx register */
5172 tmp = RREG32(DB_DEPTH_INFO);
5173
5174 mask = RLC_BUSY_STATUS | GFX_POWER_STATUS | GFX_CLOCK_STATUS | GFX_LS_STATUS;
5175 for (i = 0; i < rdev->usec_timeout; i++) {
5176 if ((RREG32(RLC_STAT) & mask) == (GFX_CLOCK_STATUS | GFX_POWER_STATUS))
5177 break;
5178 udelay(1);
5179 }
5180 }
5181}
5182
5183static void si_set_uvd_dcm(struct radeon_device *rdev,
5184 bool sw_mode)
5185{
5186 u32 tmp, tmp2;
5187
5188 tmp = RREG32(UVD_CGC_CTRL);
5189 tmp &= ~(CLK_OD_MASK | CG_DT_MASK);
5190 tmp |= DCM | CG_DT(1) | CLK_OD(4);
5191
5192 if (sw_mode) {
5193 tmp &= ~0x7ffff800;
5194 tmp2 = DYN_OR_EN | DYN_RR_EN | G_DIV_ID(7);
5195 } else {
5196 tmp |= 0x7ffff800;
5197 tmp2 = 0;
5198 }
5199
5200 WREG32(UVD_CGC_CTRL, tmp);
5201 WREG32_UVD_CTX(UVD_CGC_CTRL2, tmp2);
5202}
5203
5204void si_init_uvd_internal_cg(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5205{
5206 bool hw_mode = true;
5207
5208 if (hw_mode) {
5209 si_set_uvd_dcm(rdev, false);
5210 } else {
5211 u32 tmp = RREG32(UVD_CGC_CTRL);
5212 tmp &= ~DCM;
5213 WREG32(UVD_CGC_CTRL, tmp);
5214 }
5215}
5216
5217static u32 si_halt_rlc(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5218{
5219 u32 data, orig;
5220
5221 orig = data = RREG32(RLC_CNTL);
5222
5223 if (data & RLC_ENABLE) {
5224 data &= ~RLC_ENABLE;
5225 WREG32(RLC_CNTL, data);
5226
5227 si_wait_for_rlc_serdes(rdev);
5228 }
5229
5230 return orig;
5231}
5232
5233static void si_update_rlc(struct radeon_device *rdev, u32 rlc)
5234{
5235 u32 tmp;
5236
5237 tmp = RREG32(RLC_CNTL);
5238 if (tmp != rlc)
5239 WREG32(RLC_CNTL, rlc);
5240}
5241
5242static void si_enable_dma_pg(struct radeon_device *rdev, bool enable)
5243{
5244 u32 data, orig;
5245
5246 orig = data = RREG32(DMA_PG);
5247 if (enable && (rdev->pg_flags & RADEON_PG_SUPPORT_SDMA))
5248 data |= PG_CNTL_ENABLE;
5249 else
5250 data &= ~PG_CNTL_ENABLE;
5251 if (orig != data)
5252 WREG32(DMA_PG, data);
5253}
5254
5255static void si_init_dma_pg(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5256{
5257 u32 tmp;
5258
5259 WREG32(DMA_PGFSM_WRITE, 0x00002000);
5260 WREG32(DMA_PGFSM_CONFIG, 0x100010ff);
5261
5262 for (tmp = 0; tmp < 5; tmp++)
5263 WREG32(DMA_PGFSM_WRITE, 0);
5264}
5265
5266static void si_enable_gfx_cgpg(struct radeon_device *rdev,
5267 bool enable)
5268{
5269 u32 tmp;
5270
5271 if (enable && (rdev->pg_flags & RADEON_PG_SUPPORT_GFX_PG)) {
5272 tmp = RLC_PUD(0x10) | RLC_PDD(0x10) | RLC_TTPD(0x10) | RLC_MSD(0x10);
5273 WREG32(RLC_TTOP_D, tmp);
5274
5275 tmp = RREG32(RLC_PG_CNTL);
5276 tmp |= GFX_PG_ENABLE;
5277 WREG32(RLC_PG_CNTL, tmp);
5278
5279 tmp = RREG32(RLC_AUTO_PG_CTRL);
5280 tmp |= AUTO_PG_EN;
5281 WREG32(RLC_AUTO_PG_CTRL, tmp);
5282 } else {
5283 tmp = RREG32(RLC_AUTO_PG_CTRL);
5284 tmp &= ~AUTO_PG_EN;
5285 WREG32(RLC_AUTO_PG_CTRL, tmp);
5286
5287 tmp = RREG32(DB_RENDER_CONTROL);
5288 }
5289}
5290
5291static void si_init_gfx_cgpg(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5292{
5293 u32 tmp;
5294
5295 WREG32(RLC_SAVE_AND_RESTORE_BASE, rdev->rlc.save_restore_gpu_addr >> 8);
5296
5297 tmp = RREG32(RLC_PG_CNTL);
5298 tmp |= GFX_PG_SRC;
5299 WREG32(RLC_PG_CNTL, tmp);
5300
5301 WREG32(RLC_CLEAR_STATE_RESTORE_BASE, rdev->rlc.clear_state_gpu_addr >> 8);
5302
5303 tmp = RREG32(RLC_AUTO_PG_CTRL);
5304
5305 tmp &= ~GRBM_REG_SGIT_MASK;
5306 tmp |= GRBM_REG_SGIT(0x700);
5307 tmp &= ~PG_AFTER_GRBM_REG_ST_MASK;
5308 WREG32(RLC_AUTO_PG_CTRL, tmp);
5309}
5310
5311static u32 si_get_cu_active_bitmap(struct radeon_device *rdev, u32 se, u32 sh)
5312{
5313 u32 mask = 0, tmp, tmp1;
5314 int i;
5315
5316 si_select_se_sh(rdev, se, sh);
5317 tmp = RREG32(CC_GC_SHADER_ARRAY_CONFIG);
5318 tmp1 = RREG32(GC_USER_SHADER_ARRAY_CONFIG);
5319 si_select_se_sh(rdev, 0xffffffff, 0xffffffff);
5320
5321 tmp &= 0xffff0000;
5322
5323 tmp |= tmp1;
5324 tmp >>= 16;
5325
5326 for (i = 0; i < rdev->config.si.max_cu_per_sh; i ++) {
5327 mask <<= 1;
5328 mask |= 1;
5329 }
5330
5331 return (~tmp) & mask;
5332}
5333
5334static void si_init_ao_cu_mask(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5335{
5336 u32 i, j, k, active_cu_number = 0;
5337 u32 mask, counter, cu_bitmap;
5338 u32 tmp = 0;
5339
5340 for (i = 0; i < rdev->config.si.max_shader_engines; i++) {
5341 for (j = 0; j < rdev->config.si.max_sh_per_se; j++) {
5342 mask = 1;
5343 cu_bitmap = 0;
5344 counter = 0;
5345 for (k = 0; k < rdev->config.si.max_cu_per_sh; k++) {
5346 if (si_get_cu_active_bitmap(rdev, i, j) & mask) {
5347 if (counter < 2)
5348 cu_bitmap |= mask;
5349 counter++;
5350 }
5351 mask <<= 1;
5352 }
5353
5354 active_cu_number += counter;
5355 tmp |= (cu_bitmap << (i * 16 + j * 8));
5356 }
5357 }
5358
5359 WREG32(RLC_PG_AO_CU_MASK, tmp);
5360
5361 tmp = RREG32(RLC_MAX_PG_CU);
5362 tmp &= ~MAX_PU_CU_MASK;
5363 tmp |= MAX_PU_CU(active_cu_number);
5364 WREG32(RLC_MAX_PG_CU, tmp);
5365}
5366
5367static void si_enable_cgcg(struct radeon_device *rdev,
5368 bool enable)
5369{
5370 u32 data, orig, tmp;
5371
5372 orig = data = RREG32(RLC_CGCG_CGLS_CTRL);
5373
5374 if (enable && (rdev->cg_flags & RADEON_CG_SUPPORT_GFX_CGCG)) {
5375 si_enable_gui_idle_interrupt(rdev, true);
5376
5377 WREG32(RLC_GCPM_GENERAL_3, 0x00000080);
5378
5379 tmp = si_halt_rlc(rdev);
5380
5381 WREG32(RLC_SERDES_WR_MASTER_MASK_0, 0xffffffff);
5382 WREG32(RLC_SERDES_WR_MASTER_MASK_1, 0xffffffff);
5383 WREG32(RLC_SERDES_WR_CTRL, 0x00b000ff);
5384
5385 si_wait_for_rlc_serdes(rdev);
5386
5387 si_update_rlc(rdev, tmp);
5388
5389 WREG32(RLC_SERDES_WR_CTRL, 0x007000ff);
5390
5391 data |= CGCG_EN | CGLS_EN;
5392 } else {
5393 si_enable_gui_idle_interrupt(rdev, false);
5394
5395 RREG32(CB_CGTT_SCLK_CTRL);
5396 RREG32(CB_CGTT_SCLK_CTRL);
5397 RREG32(CB_CGTT_SCLK_CTRL);
5398 RREG32(CB_CGTT_SCLK_CTRL);
5399
5400 data &= ~(CGCG_EN | CGLS_EN);
5401 }
5402
5403 if (orig != data)
5404 WREG32(RLC_CGCG_CGLS_CTRL, data);
5405}
5406
5407static void si_enable_mgcg(struct radeon_device *rdev,
5408 bool enable)
5409{
5410 u32 data, orig, tmp = 0;
5411
5412 if (enable && (rdev->cg_flags & RADEON_CG_SUPPORT_GFX_MGCG)) {
5413 orig = data = RREG32(CGTS_SM_CTRL_REG);
5414 data = 0x96940200;
5415 if (orig != data)
5416 WREG32(CGTS_SM_CTRL_REG, data);
5417
5418 if (rdev->cg_flags & RADEON_CG_SUPPORT_GFX_CP_LS) {
5419 orig = data = RREG32(CP_MEM_SLP_CNTL);
5420 data |= CP_MEM_LS_EN;
5421 if (orig != data)
5422 WREG32(CP_MEM_SLP_CNTL, data);
5423 }
5424
5425 orig = data = RREG32(RLC_CGTT_MGCG_OVERRIDE);
5426 data &= 0xffffffc0;
5427 if (orig != data)
5428 WREG32(RLC_CGTT_MGCG_OVERRIDE, data);
5429
5430 tmp = si_halt_rlc(rdev);
5431
5432 WREG32(RLC_SERDES_WR_MASTER_MASK_0, 0xffffffff);
5433 WREG32(RLC_SERDES_WR_MASTER_MASK_1, 0xffffffff);
5434 WREG32(RLC_SERDES_WR_CTRL, 0x00d000ff);
5435
5436 si_update_rlc(rdev, tmp);
5437 } else {
5438 orig = data = RREG32(RLC_CGTT_MGCG_OVERRIDE);
5439 data |= 0x00000003;
5440 if (orig != data)
5441 WREG32(RLC_CGTT_MGCG_OVERRIDE, data);
5442
5443 data = RREG32(CP_MEM_SLP_CNTL);
5444 if (data & CP_MEM_LS_EN) {
5445 data &= ~CP_MEM_LS_EN;
5446 WREG32(CP_MEM_SLP_CNTL, data);
5447 }
5448 orig = data = RREG32(CGTS_SM_CTRL_REG);
5449 data |= LS_OVERRIDE | OVERRIDE;
5450 if (orig != data)
5451 WREG32(CGTS_SM_CTRL_REG, data);
5452
5453 tmp = si_halt_rlc(rdev);
5454
5455 WREG32(RLC_SERDES_WR_MASTER_MASK_0, 0xffffffff);
5456 WREG32(RLC_SERDES_WR_MASTER_MASK_1, 0xffffffff);
5457 WREG32(RLC_SERDES_WR_CTRL, 0x00e000ff);
5458
5459 si_update_rlc(rdev, tmp);
5460 }
5461}
5462
5463static void si_enable_uvd_mgcg(struct radeon_device *rdev,
5464 bool enable)
5465{
5466 u32 orig, data, tmp;
5467
5468 if (enable && (rdev->cg_flags & RADEON_CG_SUPPORT_UVD_MGCG)) {
5469 tmp = RREG32_UVD_CTX(UVD_CGC_MEM_CTRL);
5470 tmp |= 0x3fff;
5471 WREG32_UVD_CTX(UVD_CGC_MEM_CTRL, tmp);
5472
5473 orig = data = RREG32(UVD_CGC_CTRL);
5474 data |= DCM;
5475 if (orig != data)
5476 WREG32(UVD_CGC_CTRL, data);
5477
5478 WREG32_SMC(SMC_CG_IND_START + CG_CGTT_LOCAL_0, 0);
5479 WREG32_SMC(SMC_CG_IND_START + CG_CGTT_LOCAL_1, 0);
5480 } else {
5481 tmp = RREG32_UVD_CTX(UVD_CGC_MEM_CTRL);
5482 tmp &= ~0x3fff;
5483 WREG32_UVD_CTX(UVD_CGC_MEM_CTRL, tmp);
5484
5485 orig = data = RREG32(UVD_CGC_CTRL);
5486 data &= ~DCM;
5487 if (orig != data)
5488 WREG32(UVD_CGC_CTRL, data);
5489
5490 WREG32_SMC(SMC_CG_IND_START + CG_CGTT_LOCAL_0, 0xffffffff);
5491 WREG32_SMC(SMC_CG_IND_START + CG_CGTT_LOCAL_1, 0xffffffff);
5492 }
5493}

5508static void si_enable_mc_ls(struct radeon_device *rdev,
5509 bool enable)
5510{

5512 u32 orig, data;
5513
5514 for (i = 0; i < ARRAY_SIZE(mc_cg_registers); i++) {
5515 orig = data = RREG32(mc_cg_registers[i]);
5516 if (enable && (rdev->cg_flags & RADEON_CG_SUPPORT_MC_LS))
5517 data |= MC_LS_ENABLE;
5518 else
5519 data &= ~MC_LS_ENABLE;
5520 if (data != orig)
5521 WREG32(mc_cg_registers[i], data);
5522 }
5523}

5533 if (enable && (rdev->cg_flags & RADEON_CG_SUPPORT_MC_MGCG))
5534 data |= MC_CG_ENABLE;

5541
5542static void si_enable_dma_mgcg(struct radeon_device *rdev,
5543 bool enable)
5544{
5545 u32 orig, data, offset;
5546 int i;
5547
5548 if (enable && (rdev->cg_flags & RADEON_CG_SUPPORT_SDMA_MGCG)) {
5549 for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
5550 if (i == 0)
5551 offset = DMA0_REGISTER_OFFSET;
5552 else
5553 offset = DMA1_REGISTER_OFFSET;
5554 orig = data = RREG32(DMA_POWER_CNTL + offset);
5555 data &= ~MEM_POWER_OVERRIDE;
5556 if (data != orig)
5557 WREG32(DMA_POWER_CNTL + offset, data);
5558 WREG32(DMA_CLK_CTRL + offset, 0x00000100);
5559 }
5560 } else {
5561 for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
5562 if (i == 0)
5563 offset = DMA0_REGISTER_OFFSET;
5564 else
5565 offset = DMA1_REGISTER_OFFSET;
5566 orig = data = RREG32(DMA_POWER_CNTL + offset);
5567 data |= MEM_POWER_OVERRIDE;
5568 if (data != orig)
5569 WREG32(DMA_POWER_CNTL + offset, data);
5570
5571 orig = data = RREG32(DMA_CLK_CTRL + offset);
5572 data = 0xff000000;
5573 if (data != orig)
5574 WREG32(DMA_CLK_CTRL + offset, data);
5575 }
5576 }
5577}
5578
5579static void si_enable_bif_mgls(struct radeon_device *rdev,
5580 bool enable)
5581{
5582 u32 orig, data;
5583
5584 orig = data = RREG32_PCIE(PCIE_CNTL2);
5585
5586 if (enable && (rdev->cg_flags & RADEON_CG_SUPPORT_BIF_LS))
5587 data |= SLV_MEM_LS_EN | MST_MEM_LS_EN |
5588 REPLAY_MEM_LS_EN | SLV_MEM_AGGRESSIVE_LS_EN;
5589 else
5590 data &= ~(SLV_MEM_LS_EN | MST_MEM_LS_EN |
5591 REPLAY_MEM_LS_EN | SLV_MEM_AGGRESSIVE_LS_EN);
5592
5593 if (orig != data)
5594 WREG32_PCIE(PCIE_CNTL2, data);
5595}

5601

5603
5604 if (enable && (rdev->cg_flags & RADEON_CG_SUPPORT_HDP_MGCG))
5605 data &= ~CLOCK_GATING_DIS;
5606 else
5607 data |= CLOCK_GATING_DIS;
5608
5609 if (orig != data)

5613static void si_enable_hdp_ls(struct radeon_device *rdev,
