5621 data |= HDP_LS_ENABLE;
5622 else
5623 data &= ~HDP_LS_ENABLE;
5624
5625 if (orig != data)
5626 WREG32(HDP_MEM_POWER_LS, data);
5627}
5628
5629static void si_update_cg(struct radeon_device *rdev,
5630 u32 block, bool enable)
5631{
5632 if (block & RADEON_CG_BLOCK_GFX) {
5633 si_enable_gui_idle_interrupt(rdev, false);
5634 /* order matters! */
5635 if (enable) {
5636 si_enable_mgcg(rdev, true);
5637 si_enable_cgcg(rdev, true);
5638 } else {
5639 si_enable_cgcg(rdev, false);
5640 si_enable_mgcg(rdev, false);
5641 }
5642 si_enable_gui_idle_interrupt(rdev, true);
5643 }
5644
5645 if (block & RADEON_CG_BLOCK_MC) {
5646 si_enable_mc_mgcg(rdev, enable);
5647 si_enable_mc_ls(rdev, enable);
5648 }
5649
5650 if (block & RADEON_CG_BLOCK_SDMA) {
5651 si_enable_dma_mgcg(rdev, enable);
5652 }
5653
5654 if (block & RADEON_CG_BLOCK_BIF) {
5655 si_enable_bif_mgls(rdev, enable);
5656 }
5657
5658 if (block & RADEON_CG_BLOCK_UVD) {
5659 if (rdev->has_uvd) {
5660 si_enable_uvd_mgcg(rdev, enable);
5661 }
5662 }
5663
5664 if (block & RADEON_CG_BLOCK_HDP) {
5665 si_enable_hdp_mgcg(rdev, enable);
5666 si_enable_hdp_ls(rdev, enable);
5667 }
5668}
5669
5670static void si_init_cg(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5671{
5672 si_update_cg(rdev, (RADEON_CG_BLOCK_GFX |
5673 RADEON_CG_BLOCK_MC |
5674 RADEON_CG_BLOCK_SDMA |
5675 RADEON_CG_BLOCK_BIF |
5676 RADEON_CG_BLOCK_HDP), true);
5677 if (rdev->has_uvd) {
5678 si_update_cg(rdev, RADEON_CG_BLOCK_UVD, true);
5679 si_init_uvd_internal_cg(rdev);
5680 }
5681}
5682
5683static void si_fini_cg(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5684{
5685 if (rdev->has_uvd) {
5686 si_update_cg(rdev, RADEON_CG_BLOCK_UVD, false);
5687 }
5688 si_update_cg(rdev, (RADEON_CG_BLOCK_GFX |
5689 RADEON_CG_BLOCK_MC |
5690 RADEON_CG_BLOCK_SDMA |
5691 RADEON_CG_BLOCK_BIF |
5692 RADEON_CG_BLOCK_HDP), false);
5693}
5694
5695u32 si_get_csb_size(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5696{
5697 u32 count = 0;
5698 const struct cs_section_def *sect = NULL;
5699 const struct cs_extent_def *ext = NULL;
5700
5701 if (rdev->rlc.cs_data == NULL)
5702 return 0;
5703
5704 /* begin clear state */
5705 count += 2;
5706 /* context control state */
5707 count += 3;
5708
5709 for (sect = rdev->rlc.cs_data; sect->section != NULL; ++sect) {
5710 for (ext = sect->section; ext->extent != NULL; ++ext) {
5711 if (sect->id == SECT_CONTEXT)
5712 count += 2 + ext->reg_count;
5713 else
5714 return 0;
5715 }
5716 }
5717 /* pa_sc_raster_config */
5718 count += 3;
5719 /* end clear state */
5720 count += 2;
5721 /* clear state */
5722 count += 2;
5723
5724 return count;
5725}
5726
5727void si_get_csb_buffer(struct radeon_device *rdev, volatile u32 *buffer)
5728{
5729 u32 count = 0, i;
5730 const struct cs_section_def *sect = NULL;
5731 const struct cs_extent_def *ext = NULL;
5732
5733 if (rdev->rlc.cs_data == NULL)
5734 return;
5735 if (buffer == NULL)
5736 return;
5737
5738 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(PACKET3(PACKET3_PREAMBLE_CNTL, 0));
5739 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(PACKET3_PREAMBLE_BEGIN_CLEAR_STATE);
5740
5741 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(PACKET3(PACKET3_CONTEXT_CONTROL, 1));
5742 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(0x80000000);
5743 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(0x80000000);
5744
5745 for (sect = rdev->rlc.cs_data; sect->section != NULL; ++sect) {
5746 for (ext = sect->section; ext->extent != NULL; ++ext) {
5747 if (sect->id == SECT_CONTEXT) {
5748 buffer[count++] =
5749 cpu_to_le32(PACKET3(PACKET3_SET_CONTEXT_REG, ext->reg_count));
5750 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(ext->reg_index - 0xa000);
5751 for (i = 0; i < ext->reg_count; i++)
5752 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(ext->extent[i]);
5753 } else {
5754 return;
5755 }
5756 }
5757 }
5758
5759 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(PACKET3(PACKET3_SET_CONTEXT_REG, 1));
5760 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(PA_SC_RASTER_CONFIG - PACKET3_SET_CONTEXT_REG_START);
5761 switch (rdev->family) {
5762 case CHIP_TAHITI:
5763 case CHIP_PITCAIRN:
5764 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(0x2a00126a);
5765 break;
5766 case CHIP_VERDE:
5767 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(0x0000124a);
5768 break;
5769 case CHIP_OLAND:
5770 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(0x00000082);
5771 break;
5772 case CHIP_HAINAN:
5773 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(0x00000000);
5774 break;
5775 default:
5776 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(0x00000000);
5777 break;
5778 }
5779
5780 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(PACKET3(PACKET3_PREAMBLE_CNTL, 0));
5781 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(PACKET3_PREAMBLE_END_CLEAR_STATE);
5782
5783 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(PACKET3(PACKET3_CLEAR_STATE, 0));
5784 buffer[count++] = cpu_to_le32(0);
5785}
5786
5787static void si_init_pg(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5788{
5789 if (rdev->pg_flags) {
5790 if (rdev->pg_flags & RADEON_PG_SUPPORT_SDMA) {
5791 si_init_dma_pg(rdev);
5792 }
5793 si_init_ao_cu_mask(rdev);
5794 if (rdev->pg_flags & RADEON_PG_SUPPORT_GFX_PG) {
5795 si_init_gfx_cgpg(rdev);
5796 } else {
5797 WREG32(RLC_SAVE_AND_RESTORE_BASE, rdev->rlc.save_restore_gpu_addr >> 8);
5798 WREG32(RLC_CLEAR_STATE_RESTORE_BASE, rdev->rlc.clear_state_gpu_addr >> 8);
5799 }
5800 si_enable_dma_pg(rdev, true);
5801 si_enable_gfx_cgpg(rdev, true);
5802 } else {
5803 WREG32(RLC_SAVE_AND_RESTORE_BASE, rdev->rlc.save_restore_gpu_addr >> 8);
5804 WREG32(RLC_CLEAR_STATE_RESTORE_BASE, rdev->rlc.clear_state_gpu_addr >> 8);
5805 }
5806}
5807
5808static void si_fini_pg(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5809{
5810 if (rdev->pg_flags) {
5811 si_enable_dma_pg(rdev, false);
5812 si_enable_gfx_cgpg(rdev, false);
5813 }
5814}
5815
5816/*
5817 * RLC
5818 */
5819void si_rlc_reset(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5820{
5821 u32 tmp = RREG32(GRBM_SOFT_RESET);
5822
5823 tmp |= SOFT_RESET_RLC;
5824 WREG32(GRBM_SOFT_RESET, tmp);
5825 udelay(50);
5826 tmp &= ~SOFT_RESET_RLC;
5827 WREG32(GRBM_SOFT_RESET, tmp);
5828 udelay(50);
5829}
5830
5831static void si_rlc_stop(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5832{
5833 WREG32(RLC_CNTL, 0);
5834
5835 si_enable_gui_idle_interrupt(rdev, false);
5836
5837 si_wait_for_rlc_serdes(rdev);
5838}
5839
5840static void si_rlc_start(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5841{
5842 WREG32(RLC_CNTL, RLC_ENABLE);
5843
5844 si_enable_gui_idle_interrupt(rdev, true);
5845
5846 udelay(50);
5847}
5848
5849static bool si_lbpw_supported(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5850{
5851 u32 tmp;
5852
5853 /* Enable LBPW only for DDR3 */
5854 tmp = RREG32(MC_SEQ_MISC0);
5855 if ((tmp & 0xF0000000) == 0xB0000000)
5856 return true;
5857 return false;
5858}
5859
5860static void si_enable_lbpw(struct radeon_device *rdev, bool enable)
5861{
5862 u32 tmp;
5863
5864 tmp = RREG32(RLC_LB_CNTL);
5865 if (enable)
5866 tmp |= LOAD_BALANCE_ENABLE;
5867 else
5868 tmp &= ~LOAD_BALANCE_ENABLE;
5869 WREG32(RLC_LB_CNTL, tmp);
5870
5871 if (!enable) {
5872 si_select_se_sh(rdev, 0xffffffff, 0xffffffff);
5873 WREG32(SPI_LB_CU_MASK, 0x00ff);
5874 }
5875}
5876
5877static int si_rlc_resume(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5878{
5879 u32 i;
5880
5881 if (!rdev->rlc_fw)
5882 return -EINVAL;
5883
5884 si_rlc_stop(rdev);
5885
5886 si_rlc_reset(rdev);
5887
5888 si_init_pg(rdev);
5889
5890 si_init_cg(rdev);
5891
5892 WREG32(RLC_RL_BASE, 0);
5893 WREG32(RLC_RL_SIZE, 0);
5894 WREG32(RLC_LB_CNTL, 0);
5895 WREG32(RLC_LB_CNTR_MAX, 0xffffffff);
5896 WREG32(RLC_LB_CNTR_INIT, 0);
5897 WREG32(RLC_LB_INIT_CU_MASK, 0xffffffff);
5898
5899 WREG32(RLC_MC_CNTL, 0);
5900 WREG32(RLC_UCODE_CNTL, 0);
5901
5902 if (rdev->new_fw) {
5903 const struct rlc_firmware_header_v1_0 *hdr =
5904 (const struct rlc_firmware_header_v1_0 *)rdev->rlc_fw->data;
5905 u32 fw_size = le32_to_cpu(hdr->header.ucode_size_bytes) / 4;
5906 const __le32 *fw_data = (const __le32 *)
5907 (rdev->rlc_fw->data + le32_to_cpu(hdr->header.ucode_array_offset_bytes));
5908
5909 radeon_ucode_print_rlc_hdr(&hdr->header);
5910
5911 for (i = 0; i < fw_size; i++) {
5912 WREG32(RLC_UCODE_ADDR, i);
5913 WREG32(RLC_UCODE_DATA, le32_to_cpup(fw_data++));
5914 }
5915 } else {
5916 const __be32 *fw_data =
5917 (const __be32 *)rdev->rlc_fw->data;
5918 for (i = 0; i < SI_RLC_UCODE_SIZE; i++) {
5919 WREG32(RLC_UCODE_ADDR, i);
5920 WREG32(RLC_UCODE_DATA, be32_to_cpup(fw_data++));
5921 }
5922 }
5923 WREG32(RLC_UCODE_ADDR, 0);
5924
5925 si_enable_lbpw(rdev, si_lbpw_supported(rdev));
5926
5927 si_rlc_start(rdev);
5928
5929 return 0;
5930}
5931
5932static void si_enable_interrupts(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5933{
5934 u32 ih_cntl = RREG32(IH_CNTL);
5935 u32 ih_rb_cntl = RREG32(IH_RB_CNTL);
5936
5937 ih_cntl |= ENABLE_INTR;
5938 ih_rb_cntl |= IH_RB_ENABLE;
5939 WREG32(IH_CNTL, ih_cntl);
5940 WREG32(IH_RB_CNTL, ih_rb_cntl);
5941 rdev->ih.enabled = true;
5942}
5943
5944static void si_disable_interrupts(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5945{
5946 u32 ih_rb_cntl = RREG32(IH_RB_CNTL);
5947 u32 ih_cntl = RREG32(IH_CNTL);
5948
5949 ih_rb_cntl &= ~IH_RB_ENABLE;
5950 ih_cntl &= ~ENABLE_INTR;
5951 WREG32(IH_RB_CNTL, ih_rb_cntl);
5952 WREG32(IH_CNTL, ih_cntl);
5953 /* set rptr, wptr to 0 */
5954 WREG32(IH_RB_RPTR, 0);
5955 WREG32(IH_RB_WPTR, 0);
5956 rdev->ih.enabled = false;
5957 rdev->ih.rptr = 0;
5958}
5959
5960static void si_disable_interrupt_state(struct radeon_device *rdev)
5961{
5962 u32 tmp;
5963
5964 tmp = RREG32(CP_INT_CNTL_RING0) &
5965 (CNTX_BUSY_INT_ENABLE | CNTX_EMPTY_INT_ENABLE);
5966 WREG32(CP_INT_CNTL_RING0, tmp);
5967 WREG32(CP_INT_CNTL_RING1, 0);
5968 WREG32(CP_INT_CNTL_RING2, 0);
5969 tmp = RREG32(DMA_CNTL + DMA0_REGISTER_OFFSET) & ~TRAP_ENABLE;
5970 WREG32(DMA_CNTL + DMA0_REGISTER_OFFSET, tmp);
5971 tmp = RREG32(DMA_CNTL + DMA1_REGISTER_OFFSET) & ~TRAP_ENABLE;
5972 WREG32(DMA_CNTL + DMA1_REGISTER_OFFSET, tmp);
5973 WREG32(GRBM_INT_CNTL, 0);
5974 WREG32(SRBM_INT_CNTL, 0);
5975 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 2) {
5976 WREG32(INT_MASK + EVERGREEN_CRTC0_REGISTER_OFFSET, 0);
5977 WREG32(INT_MASK + EVERGREEN_CRTC1_REGISTER_OFFSET, 0);
5978 }
5979 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 4) {
5980 WREG32(INT_MASK + EVERGREEN_CRTC2_REGISTER_OFFSET, 0);
5981 WREG32(INT_MASK + EVERGREEN_CRTC3_REGISTER_OFFSET, 0);
5982 }
5983 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 6) {
5984 WREG32(INT_MASK + EVERGREEN_CRTC4_REGISTER_OFFSET, 0);
5985 WREG32(INT_MASK + EVERGREEN_CRTC5_REGISTER_OFFSET, 0);
5986 }
5987
5988 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 2) {
5989 WREG32(GRPH_INT_CONTROL + EVERGREEN_CRTC0_REGISTER_OFFSET, 0);
5990 WREG32(GRPH_INT_CONTROL + EVERGREEN_CRTC1_REGISTER_OFFSET, 0);
5991 }
5992 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 4) {
5993 WREG32(GRPH_INT_CONTROL + EVERGREEN_CRTC2_REGISTER_OFFSET, 0);
5994 WREG32(GRPH_INT_CONTROL + EVERGREEN_CRTC3_REGISTER_OFFSET, 0);
5995 }
5996 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 6) {
5997 WREG32(GRPH_INT_CONTROL + EVERGREEN_CRTC4_REGISTER_OFFSET, 0);
5998 WREG32(GRPH_INT_CONTROL + EVERGREEN_CRTC5_REGISTER_OFFSET, 0);
5999 }
6000
6001 if (!ASIC_IS_NODCE(rdev)) {
6002 WREG32(DAC_AUTODETECT_INT_CONTROL, 0);
6003
6004 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD1_INT_CONTROL) & DC_HPDx_INT_POLARITY;
6005 WREG32(DC_HPD1_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6006 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD2_INT_CONTROL) & DC_HPDx_INT_POLARITY;
6007 WREG32(DC_HPD2_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6008 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD3_INT_CONTROL) & DC_HPDx_INT_POLARITY;
6009 WREG32(DC_HPD3_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6010 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD4_INT_CONTROL) & DC_HPDx_INT_POLARITY;
6011 WREG32(DC_HPD4_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6012 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD5_INT_CONTROL) & DC_HPDx_INT_POLARITY;
6013 WREG32(DC_HPD5_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6014 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD6_INT_CONTROL) & DC_HPDx_INT_POLARITY;
6015 WREG32(DC_HPD6_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6016 }
6017}
6018
6019static int si_irq_init(struct radeon_device *rdev)
6020{
6021 int ret = 0;
6022 int rb_bufsz;
6023 u32 interrupt_cntl, ih_cntl, ih_rb_cntl;
6024
6025 /* allocate ring */
6026 ret = r600_ih_ring_alloc(rdev);
6027 if (ret)
6028 return ret;
6029
6030 /* disable irqs */
6031 si_disable_interrupts(rdev);
6032
6033 /* init rlc */
6034 ret = si_rlc_resume(rdev);
6035 if (ret) {
6036 r600_ih_ring_fini(rdev);
6037 return ret;
6038 }
6039
6040 /* setup interrupt control */
6041 /* set dummy read address to ring address */
6042 WREG32(INTERRUPT_CNTL2, rdev->ih.gpu_addr >> 8);
6043 interrupt_cntl = RREG32(INTERRUPT_CNTL);
6044 /* IH_DUMMY_RD_OVERRIDE=0 - dummy read disabled with msi, enabled without msi
6045 * IH_DUMMY_RD_OVERRIDE=1 - dummy read controlled by IH_DUMMY_RD_EN
6046 */
6047 interrupt_cntl &= ~IH_DUMMY_RD_OVERRIDE;
6048 /* IH_REQ_NONSNOOP_EN=1 if ring is in non-cacheable memory, e.g., vram */
6049 interrupt_cntl &= ~IH_REQ_NONSNOOP_EN;
6050 WREG32(INTERRUPT_CNTL, interrupt_cntl);
6051
6052 WREG32(IH_RB_BASE, rdev->ih.gpu_addr >> 8);
6053 rb_bufsz = order_base_2(rdev->ih.ring_size / 4);
6054
6055 ih_rb_cntl = (IH_WPTR_OVERFLOW_ENABLE |
6056 IH_WPTR_OVERFLOW_CLEAR |
6057 (rb_bufsz << 1));
6058
6059 if (rdev->wb.enabled)
6060 ih_rb_cntl |= IH_WPTR_WRITEBACK_ENABLE;
6061
6062 /* set the writeback address whether it's enabled or not */
6063 WREG32(IH_RB_WPTR_ADDR_LO, (rdev->wb.gpu_addr + R600_WB_IH_WPTR_OFFSET) & 0xFFFFFFFC);
6064 WREG32(IH_RB_WPTR_ADDR_HI, upper_32_bits(rdev->wb.gpu_addr + R600_WB_IH_WPTR_OFFSET) & 0xFF);
6065
6066 WREG32(IH_RB_CNTL, ih_rb_cntl);
6067
6068 /* set rptr, wptr to 0 */
6069 WREG32(IH_RB_RPTR, 0);
6070 WREG32(IH_RB_WPTR, 0);
6071
6072 /* Default settings for IH_CNTL (disabled at first) */
6073 ih_cntl = MC_WRREQ_CREDIT(0x10) | MC_WR_CLEAN_CNT(0x10) | MC_VMID(0);
6074 /* RPTR_REARM only works if msi's are enabled */
6075 if (rdev->msi_enabled)
6076 ih_cntl |= RPTR_REARM;
6077 WREG32(IH_CNTL, ih_cntl);
6078
6079 /* force the active interrupt state to all disabled */
6080 si_disable_interrupt_state(rdev);
6081
6082 pci_set_master(rdev->pdev);
6083
6084 /* enable irqs */
6085 si_enable_interrupts(rdev);
6086
6087 return ret;
6088}
6089
6090int si_irq_set(struct radeon_device *rdev)
6091{
6092 u32 cp_int_cntl;
6093 u32 cp_int_cntl1 = 0, cp_int_cntl2 = 0;
6094 u32 crtc1 = 0, crtc2 = 0, crtc3 = 0, crtc4 = 0, crtc5 = 0, crtc6 = 0;
6095 u32 hpd1 = 0, hpd2 = 0, hpd3 = 0, hpd4 = 0, hpd5 = 0, hpd6 = 0;
6096 u32 grbm_int_cntl = 0;
6097 u32 dma_cntl, dma_cntl1;
6098 u32 thermal_int = 0;
6099
6100 if (!rdev->irq.installed) {
6101 WARN(1, "Can't enable IRQ/MSI because no handler is installed\n");
6102 return -EINVAL;
6103 }
6104 /* don't enable anything if the ih is disabled */
6105 if (!rdev->ih.enabled) {
6106 si_disable_interrupts(rdev);
6107 /* force the active interrupt state to all disabled */
6108 si_disable_interrupt_state(rdev);
6109 return 0;
6110 }
6111
6112 cp_int_cntl = RREG32(CP_INT_CNTL_RING0) &
6113 (CNTX_BUSY_INT_ENABLE | CNTX_EMPTY_INT_ENABLE);
6114
6115 if (!ASIC_IS_NODCE(rdev)) {
6116 hpd1 = RREG32(DC_HPD1_INT_CONTROL) & ~(DC_HPDx_INT_EN | DC_HPDx_RX_INT_EN);
6117 hpd2 = RREG32(DC_HPD2_INT_CONTROL) & ~(DC_HPDx_INT_EN | DC_HPDx_RX_INT_EN);
6118 hpd3 = RREG32(DC_HPD3_INT_CONTROL) & ~(DC_HPDx_INT_EN | DC_HPDx_RX_INT_EN);
6119 hpd4 = RREG32(DC_HPD4_INT_CONTROL) & ~(DC_HPDx_INT_EN | DC_HPDx_RX_INT_EN);
6120 hpd5 = RREG32(DC_HPD5_INT_CONTROL) & ~(DC_HPDx_INT_EN | DC_HPDx_RX_INT_EN);
6121 hpd6 = RREG32(DC_HPD6_INT_CONTROL) & ~(DC_HPDx_INT_EN | DC_HPDx_RX_INT_EN);
6122 }
6123
6124 dma_cntl = RREG32(DMA_CNTL + DMA0_REGISTER_OFFSET) & ~TRAP_ENABLE;
6125 dma_cntl1 = RREG32(DMA_CNTL + DMA1_REGISTER_OFFSET) & ~TRAP_ENABLE;
6126
6127 thermal_int = RREG32(CG_THERMAL_INT) &
6128 ~(THERM_INT_MASK_HIGH | THERM_INT_MASK_LOW);
6129
6130 /* enable CP interrupts on all rings */
6131 if (atomic_read(&rdev->irq.ring_int[RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX])) {
6132 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: sw int gfx\n");
6133 cp_int_cntl |= TIME_STAMP_INT_ENABLE;
6134 }
6135 if (atomic_read(&rdev->irq.ring_int[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX])) {
6136 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: sw int cp1\n");
6137 cp_int_cntl1 |= TIME_STAMP_INT_ENABLE;
6138 }
6139 if (atomic_read(&rdev->irq.ring_int[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX])) {
6140 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: sw int cp2\n");
6141 cp_int_cntl2 |= TIME_STAMP_INT_ENABLE;
6142 }
6143 if (atomic_read(&rdev->irq.ring_int[R600_RING_TYPE_DMA_INDEX])) {
6144 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: sw int dma\n");
6145 dma_cntl |= TRAP_ENABLE;
6146 }
6147
6148 if (atomic_read(&rdev->irq.ring_int[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_DMA1_INDEX])) {
6149 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: sw int dma1\n");
6150 dma_cntl1 |= TRAP_ENABLE;
6151 }
6152 if (rdev->irq.crtc_vblank_int[0] ||
6153 atomic_read(&rdev->irq.pflip[0])) {
6154 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: vblank 0\n");
6155 crtc1 |= VBLANK_INT_MASK;
6156 }
6157 if (rdev->irq.crtc_vblank_int[1] ||
6158 atomic_read(&rdev->irq.pflip[1])) {
6159 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: vblank 1\n");
6160 crtc2 |= VBLANK_INT_MASK;
6161 }
6162 if (rdev->irq.crtc_vblank_int[2] ||
6163 atomic_read(&rdev->irq.pflip[2])) {
6164 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: vblank 2\n");
6165 crtc3 |= VBLANK_INT_MASK;
6166 }
6167 if (rdev->irq.crtc_vblank_int[3] ||
6168 atomic_read(&rdev->irq.pflip[3])) {
6169 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: vblank 3\n");
6170 crtc4 |= VBLANK_INT_MASK;
6171 }
6172 if (rdev->irq.crtc_vblank_int[4] ||
6173 atomic_read(&rdev->irq.pflip[4])) {
6174 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: vblank 4\n");
6175 crtc5 |= VBLANK_INT_MASK;
6176 }
6177 if (rdev->irq.crtc_vblank_int[5] ||
6178 atomic_read(&rdev->irq.pflip[5])) {
6179 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: vblank 5\n");
6180 crtc6 |= VBLANK_INT_MASK;
6181 }
6182 if (rdev->irq.hpd[0]) {
6183 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: hpd 1\n");
6184 hpd1 |= DC_HPDx_INT_EN | DC_HPDx_RX_INT_EN;
6185 }
6186 if (rdev->irq.hpd[1]) {
6187 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: hpd 2\n");
6188 hpd2 |= DC_HPDx_INT_EN | DC_HPDx_RX_INT_EN;
6189 }
6190 if (rdev->irq.hpd[2]) {
6191 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: hpd 3\n");
6192 hpd3 |= DC_HPDx_INT_EN | DC_HPDx_RX_INT_EN;
6193 }
6194 if (rdev->irq.hpd[3]) {
6195 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: hpd 4\n");
6196 hpd4 |= DC_HPDx_INT_EN | DC_HPDx_RX_INT_EN;
6197 }
6198 if (rdev->irq.hpd[4]) {
6199 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: hpd 5\n");
6200 hpd5 |= DC_HPDx_INT_EN | DC_HPDx_RX_INT_EN;
6201 }
6202 if (rdev->irq.hpd[5]) {
6203 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_set: hpd 6\n");
6204 hpd6 |= DC_HPDx_INT_EN | DC_HPDx_RX_INT_EN;
6205 }
6206
6207 WREG32(CP_INT_CNTL_RING0, cp_int_cntl);
6208 WREG32(CP_INT_CNTL_RING1, cp_int_cntl1);
6209 WREG32(CP_INT_CNTL_RING2, cp_int_cntl2);
6210
6211 WREG32(DMA_CNTL + DMA0_REGISTER_OFFSET, dma_cntl);
6212 WREG32(DMA_CNTL + DMA1_REGISTER_OFFSET, dma_cntl1);
6213
6214 WREG32(GRBM_INT_CNTL, grbm_int_cntl);
6215
6216 if (rdev->irq.dpm_thermal) {
6217 DRM_DEBUG("dpm thermal\n");
6218 thermal_int |= THERM_INT_MASK_HIGH | THERM_INT_MASK_LOW;
6219 }
6220
6221 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 2) {
6222 WREG32(INT_MASK + EVERGREEN_CRTC0_REGISTER_OFFSET, crtc1);
6223 WREG32(INT_MASK + EVERGREEN_CRTC1_REGISTER_OFFSET, crtc2);
6224 }
6225 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 4) {
6226 WREG32(INT_MASK + EVERGREEN_CRTC2_REGISTER_OFFSET, crtc3);
6227 WREG32(INT_MASK + EVERGREEN_CRTC3_REGISTER_OFFSET, crtc4);
6228 }
6229 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 6) {
6230 WREG32(INT_MASK + EVERGREEN_CRTC4_REGISTER_OFFSET, crtc5);
6231 WREG32(INT_MASK + EVERGREEN_CRTC5_REGISTER_OFFSET, crtc6);
6232 }
6233
6234 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 2) {
6235 WREG32(GRPH_INT_CONTROL + EVERGREEN_CRTC0_REGISTER_OFFSET,
6236 GRPH_PFLIP_INT_MASK);
6237 WREG32(GRPH_INT_CONTROL + EVERGREEN_CRTC1_REGISTER_OFFSET,
6238 GRPH_PFLIP_INT_MASK);
6239 }
6240 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 4) {
6241 WREG32(GRPH_INT_CONTROL + EVERGREEN_CRTC2_REGISTER_OFFSET,
6242 GRPH_PFLIP_INT_MASK);
6243 WREG32(GRPH_INT_CONTROL + EVERGREEN_CRTC3_REGISTER_OFFSET,
6244 GRPH_PFLIP_INT_MASK);
6245 }
6246 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 6) {
6247 WREG32(GRPH_INT_CONTROL + EVERGREEN_CRTC4_REGISTER_OFFSET,
6248 GRPH_PFLIP_INT_MASK);
6249 WREG32(GRPH_INT_CONTROL + EVERGREEN_CRTC5_REGISTER_OFFSET,
6250 GRPH_PFLIP_INT_MASK);
6251 }
6252
6253 if (!ASIC_IS_NODCE(rdev)) {
6254 WREG32(DC_HPD1_INT_CONTROL, hpd1);
6255 WREG32(DC_HPD2_INT_CONTROL, hpd2);
6256 WREG32(DC_HPD3_INT_CONTROL, hpd3);
6257 WREG32(DC_HPD4_INT_CONTROL, hpd4);
6258 WREG32(DC_HPD5_INT_CONTROL, hpd5);
6259 WREG32(DC_HPD6_INT_CONTROL, hpd6);
6260 }
6261
6262 WREG32(CG_THERMAL_INT, thermal_int);
6263
6264 /* posting read */
6265 RREG32(SRBM_STATUS);
6266
6267 return 0;
6268}
6269
6270static inline void si_irq_ack(struct radeon_device *rdev)
6271{
6272 u32 tmp;
6273
6274 if (ASIC_IS_NODCE(rdev))
6275 return;
6276
6277 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int = RREG32(DISP_INTERRUPT_STATUS);
6278 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont = RREG32(DISP_INTERRUPT_STATUS_CONTINUE);
6279 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 = RREG32(DISP_INTERRUPT_STATUS_CONTINUE2);
6280 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 = RREG32(DISP_INTERRUPT_STATUS_CONTINUE3);
6281 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont4 = RREG32(DISP_INTERRUPT_STATUS_CONTINUE4);
6282 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont5 = RREG32(DISP_INTERRUPT_STATUS_CONTINUE5);
6283 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.d1grph_int = RREG32(GRPH_INT_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC0_REGISTER_OFFSET);
6284 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.d2grph_int = RREG32(GRPH_INT_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC1_REGISTER_OFFSET);
6285 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 4) {
6286 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.d3grph_int = RREG32(GRPH_INT_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC2_REGISTER_OFFSET);
6287 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.d4grph_int = RREG32(GRPH_INT_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC3_REGISTER_OFFSET);
6288 }
6289 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 6) {
6290 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.d5grph_int = RREG32(GRPH_INT_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC4_REGISTER_OFFSET);
6291 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.d6grph_int = RREG32(GRPH_INT_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC5_REGISTER_OFFSET);
6292 }
6293
6294 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.d1grph_int & GRPH_PFLIP_INT_OCCURRED)
6295 WREG32(GRPH_INT_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC0_REGISTER_OFFSET, GRPH_PFLIP_INT_CLEAR);
6296 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.d2grph_int & GRPH_PFLIP_INT_OCCURRED)
6297 WREG32(GRPH_INT_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC1_REGISTER_OFFSET, GRPH_PFLIP_INT_CLEAR);
6298 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int & LB_D1_VBLANK_INTERRUPT)
6299 WREG32(VBLANK_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC0_REGISTER_OFFSET, VBLANK_ACK);
6300 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int & LB_D1_VLINE_INTERRUPT)
6301 WREG32(VLINE_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC0_REGISTER_OFFSET, VLINE_ACK);
6302 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont & LB_D2_VBLANK_INTERRUPT)
6303 WREG32(VBLANK_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC1_REGISTER_OFFSET, VBLANK_ACK);
6304 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont & LB_D2_VLINE_INTERRUPT)
6305 WREG32(VLINE_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC1_REGISTER_OFFSET, VLINE_ACK);
6306
6307 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 4) {
6308 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.d3grph_int & GRPH_PFLIP_INT_OCCURRED)
6309 WREG32(GRPH_INT_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC2_REGISTER_OFFSET, GRPH_PFLIP_INT_CLEAR);
6310 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.d4grph_int & GRPH_PFLIP_INT_OCCURRED)
6311 WREG32(GRPH_INT_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC3_REGISTER_OFFSET, GRPH_PFLIP_INT_CLEAR);
6312 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 & LB_D3_VBLANK_INTERRUPT)
6313 WREG32(VBLANK_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC2_REGISTER_OFFSET, VBLANK_ACK);
6314 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 & LB_D3_VLINE_INTERRUPT)
6315 WREG32(VLINE_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC2_REGISTER_OFFSET, VLINE_ACK);
6316 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 & LB_D4_VBLANK_INTERRUPT)
6317 WREG32(VBLANK_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC3_REGISTER_OFFSET, VBLANK_ACK);
6318 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 & LB_D4_VLINE_INTERRUPT)
6319 WREG32(VLINE_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC3_REGISTER_OFFSET, VLINE_ACK);
6320 }
6321
6322 if (rdev->num_crtc >= 6) {
6323 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.d5grph_int & GRPH_PFLIP_INT_OCCURRED)
6324 WREG32(GRPH_INT_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC4_REGISTER_OFFSET, GRPH_PFLIP_INT_CLEAR);
6325 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.d6grph_int & GRPH_PFLIP_INT_OCCURRED)
6326 WREG32(GRPH_INT_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC5_REGISTER_OFFSET, GRPH_PFLIP_INT_CLEAR);
6327 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont4 & LB_D5_VBLANK_INTERRUPT)
6328 WREG32(VBLANK_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC4_REGISTER_OFFSET, VBLANK_ACK);
6329 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont4 & LB_D5_VLINE_INTERRUPT)
6330 WREG32(VLINE_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC4_REGISTER_OFFSET, VLINE_ACK);
6331 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont5 & LB_D6_VBLANK_INTERRUPT)
6332 WREG32(VBLANK_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC5_REGISTER_OFFSET, VBLANK_ACK);
6333 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont5 & LB_D6_VLINE_INTERRUPT)
6334 WREG32(VLINE_STATUS + EVERGREEN_CRTC5_REGISTER_OFFSET, VLINE_ACK);
6335 }
6336
6337 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int & DC_HPD1_INTERRUPT) {
6338 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD1_INT_CONTROL);
6339 tmp |= DC_HPDx_INT_ACK;
6340 WREG32(DC_HPD1_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6341 }
6342 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont & DC_HPD2_INTERRUPT) {
6343 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD2_INT_CONTROL);
6344 tmp |= DC_HPDx_INT_ACK;
6345 WREG32(DC_HPD2_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6346 }
6347 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 & DC_HPD3_INTERRUPT) {
6348 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD3_INT_CONTROL);
6349 tmp |= DC_HPDx_INT_ACK;
6350 WREG32(DC_HPD3_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6351 }
6352 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 & DC_HPD4_INTERRUPT) {
6353 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD4_INT_CONTROL);
6354 tmp |= DC_HPDx_INT_ACK;
6355 WREG32(DC_HPD4_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6356 }
6357 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont4 & DC_HPD5_INTERRUPT) {
6358 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD5_INT_CONTROL);
6359 tmp |= DC_HPDx_INT_ACK;
6360 WREG32(DC_HPD5_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6361 }
6362 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont5 & DC_HPD6_INTERRUPT) {
6363 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD6_INT_CONTROL);
6364 tmp |= DC_HPDx_INT_ACK;
6365 WREG32(DC_HPD6_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6366 }
6367
6368 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int & DC_HPD1_RX_INTERRUPT) {
6369 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD1_INT_CONTROL);
6370 tmp |= DC_HPDx_RX_INT_ACK;
6371 WREG32(DC_HPD1_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6372 }
6373 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont & DC_HPD2_RX_INTERRUPT) {
6374 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD2_INT_CONTROL);
6375 tmp |= DC_HPDx_RX_INT_ACK;
6376 WREG32(DC_HPD2_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6377 }
6378 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 & DC_HPD3_RX_INTERRUPT) {
6379 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD3_INT_CONTROL);
6380 tmp |= DC_HPDx_RX_INT_ACK;
6381 WREG32(DC_HPD3_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6382 }
6383 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 & DC_HPD4_RX_INTERRUPT) {
6384 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD4_INT_CONTROL);
6385 tmp |= DC_HPDx_RX_INT_ACK;
6386 WREG32(DC_HPD4_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6387 }
6388 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont4 & DC_HPD5_RX_INTERRUPT) {
6389 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD5_INT_CONTROL);
6390 tmp |= DC_HPDx_RX_INT_ACK;
6391 WREG32(DC_HPD5_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6392 }
6393 if (rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont5 & DC_HPD6_RX_INTERRUPT) {
6394 tmp = RREG32(DC_HPD6_INT_CONTROL);
6395 tmp |= DC_HPDx_RX_INT_ACK;
6396 WREG32(DC_HPD6_INT_CONTROL, tmp);
6397 }
6398}
6399
6400static void si_irq_disable(struct radeon_device *rdev)
6401{
6402 si_disable_interrupts(rdev);
6403 /* Wait and acknowledge irq */
6404 mdelay(1);
6405 si_irq_ack(rdev);
6406 si_disable_interrupt_state(rdev);
6407}
6408
6409static void si_irq_suspend(struct radeon_device *rdev)
6410{
6411 si_irq_disable(rdev);
6412 si_rlc_stop(rdev);
6413}
6414
6415static void si_irq_fini(struct radeon_device *rdev)
6416{
6417 si_irq_suspend(rdev);
6418 r600_ih_ring_fini(rdev);
6419}
6420
6421static inline u32 si_get_ih_wptr(struct radeon_device *rdev)
6422{
6423 u32 wptr, tmp;
6424
6425 if (rdev->wb.enabled)
6426 wptr = le32_to_cpu(rdev->wb.wb[R600_WB_IH_WPTR_OFFSET/4]);
6427 else
6428 wptr = RREG32(IH_RB_WPTR);
6429
6430 if (wptr & RB_OVERFLOW) {
6431 wptr &= ~RB_OVERFLOW;
6432 /* When a ring buffer overflow happen start parsing interrupt
6433 * from the last not overwritten vector (wptr + 16). Hopefully
6434 * this should allow us to catchup.
6435 */
6436 dev_warn(rdev->dev, "IH ring buffer overflow (0x%08X, 0x%08X, 0x%08X)\n",
6437 wptr, rdev->ih.rptr, (wptr + 16) & rdev->ih.ptr_mask);
6438 rdev->ih.rptr = (wptr + 16) & rdev->ih.ptr_mask;
6439 tmp = RREG32(IH_RB_CNTL);
6440 tmp |= IH_WPTR_OVERFLOW_CLEAR;
6441 WREG32(IH_RB_CNTL, tmp);
6442 }
6443 return (wptr & rdev->ih.ptr_mask);
6444}
6445
6446/* SI IV Ring
6447 * Each IV ring entry is 128 bits:
6448 * [7:0] - interrupt source id
6449 * [31:8] - reserved
6450 * [59:32] - interrupt source data
6451 * [63:60] - reserved
6452 * [71:64] - RINGID
6453 * [79:72] - VMID
6454 * [127:80] - reserved
6455 */
6456int si_irq_process(struct radeon_device *rdev)
6457{
6458 u32 wptr;
6459 u32 rptr;
6460 u32 src_id, src_data, ring_id;
6461 u32 ring_index;
6462 bool queue_hotplug = false;
6463 bool queue_dp = false;
6464 bool queue_thermal = false;
6465 u32 status, addr;
6466
6467 if (!rdev->ih.enabled || rdev->shutdown)
6468 return IRQ_NONE;
6469
6470 wptr = si_get_ih_wptr(rdev);
6471
6472restart_ih:
6473 /* is somebody else already processing irqs? */
6474 if (atomic_xchg(&rdev->ih.lock, 1))
6475 return IRQ_NONE;
6476
6477 rptr = rdev->ih.rptr;
6478 DRM_DEBUG("si_irq_process start: rptr %d, wptr %d\n", rptr, wptr);
6479
6480 /* Order reading of wptr vs. reading of IH ring data */
6481 rmb();
6482
6483 /* display interrupts */
6484 si_irq_ack(rdev);
6485
6486 while (rptr != wptr) {
6487 /* wptr/rptr are in bytes! */
6488 ring_index = rptr / 4;
6489 src_id = le32_to_cpu(rdev->ih.ring[ring_index]) & 0xff;
6490 src_data = le32_to_cpu(rdev->ih.ring[ring_index + 1]) & 0xfffffff;
6491 ring_id = le32_to_cpu(rdev->ih.ring[ring_index + 2]) & 0xff;
6492
6493 switch (src_id) {
6494 case 1: /* D1 vblank/vline */
6495 switch (src_data) {
6496 case 0: /* D1 vblank */
6497 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int & LB_D1_VBLANK_INTERRUPT))
6498 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6499
6500 if (rdev->irq.crtc_vblank_int[0]) {
6501 drm_handle_vblank(rdev->ddev, 0);
6502#ifdef __NetBSD__
6503 spin_lock(&rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6504 rdev->pm.vblank_sync = true;
6505 DRM_SPIN_WAKEUP_ONE(&rdev->irq.vblank_queue, &rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6506 spin_unlock(&rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6507#else
6508 rdev->pm.vblank_sync = true;
6509 wake_up(&rdev->irq.vblank_queue);
6510#endif
6511 }
6512 if (atomic_read(&rdev->irq.pflip[0]))
6513 radeon_crtc_handle_vblank(rdev, 0);
6514 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int &= ~LB_D1_VBLANK_INTERRUPT;
6515 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D1 vblank\n");
6516
6517 break;
6518 case 1: /* D1 vline */
6519 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int & LB_D1_VLINE_INTERRUPT))
6520 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6521
6522 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int &= ~LB_D1_VLINE_INTERRUPT;
6523 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D1 vline\n");
6524
6525 break;
6526 default:
6527 DRM_DEBUG("Unhandled interrupt: %d %d\n", src_id, src_data);
6528 break;
6529 }
6530 break;
6531 case 2: /* D2 vblank/vline */
6532 switch (src_data) {
6533 case 0: /* D2 vblank */
6534 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont & LB_D2_VBLANK_INTERRUPT))
6535 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6536
6537 if (rdev->irq.crtc_vblank_int[1]) {
6538 drm_handle_vblank(rdev->ddev, 1);
6539#ifdef __NetBSD__
6540 spin_lock(&rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6541 rdev->pm.vblank_sync = true;
6542 DRM_SPIN_WAKEUP_ONE(&rdev->irq.vblank_queue, &rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6543 spin_unlock(&rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6544#else
6545 rdev->pm.vblank_sync = true;
6546 wake_up(&rdev->irq.vblank_queue);
6547#endif
6548 }
6549 if (atomic_read(&rdev->irq.pflip[1]))
6550 radeon_crtc_handle_vblank(rdev, 1);
6551 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont &= ~LB_D2_VBLANK_INTERRUPT;
6552 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D2 vblank\n");
6553
6554 break;
6555 case 1: /* D2 vline */
6556 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont & LB_D2_VLINE_INTERRUPT))
6557 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6558
6559 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont &= ~LB_D2_VLINE_INTERRUPT;
6560 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D2 vline\n");
6561
6562 break;
6563 default:
6564 DRM_DEBUG("Unhandled interrupt: %d %d\n", src_id, src_data);
6565 break;
6566 }
6567 break;
6568 case 3: /* D3 vblank/vline */
6569 switch (src_data) {
6570 case 0: /* D3 vblank */
6571 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 & LB_D3_VBLANK_INTERRUPT))
6572 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6573
6574 if (rdev->irq.crtc_vblank_int[2]) {
6575 drm_handle_vblank(rdev->ddev, 2);
6576#ifdef __NetBSD__
6577 spin_lock(&rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6578 rdev->pm.vblank_sync = true;
6579 DRM_SPIN_WAKEUP_ONE(&rdev->irq.vblank_queue, &rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6580 spin_unlock(&rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6581#else
6582 rdev->pm.vblank_sync = true;
6583 wake_up(&rdev->irq.vblank_queue);
6584#endif
6585 }
6586 if (atomic_read(&rdev->irq.pflip[2]))
6587 radeon_crtc_handle_vblank(rdev, 2);
6588 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 &= ~LB_D3_VBLANK_INTERRUPT;
6589 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D3 vblank\n");
6590
6591 break;
6592 case 1: /* D3 vline */
6593 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 & LB_D3_VLINE_INTERRUPT))
6594 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6595
6596 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 &= ~LB_D3_VLINE_INTERRUPT;
6597 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D3 vline\n");
6598
6599 break;
6600 default:
6601 DRM_DEBUG("Unhandled interrupt: %d %d\n", src_id, src_data);
6602 break;
6603 }
6604 break;
6605 case 4: /* D4 vblank/vline */
6606 switch (src_data) {
6607 case 0: /* D4 vblank */
6608 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 & LB_D4_VBLANK_INTERRUPT))
6609 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6610
6611 if (rdev->irq.crtc_vblank_int[3]) {
6612 drm_handle_vblank(rdev->ddev, 3);
6613#ifdef __NetBSD__
6614 spin_lock(&rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6615 rdev->pm.vblank_sync = true;
6616 DRM_SPIN_WAKEUP_ONE(&rdev->irq.vblank_queue, &rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6617 spin_unlock(&rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6618#else
6619 rdev->pm.vblank_sync = true;
6620 wake_up(&rdev->irq.vblank_queue);
6621#endif
6622 }
6623 if (atomic_read(&rdev->irq.pflip[3]))
6624 radeon_crtc_handle_vblank(rdev, 3);
6625 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 &= ~LB_D4_VBLANK_INTERRUPT;
6626 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D4 vblank\n");
6627
6628 break;
6629 case 1: /* D4 vline */
6630 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 & LB_D4_VLINE_INTERRUPT))
6631 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6632
6633 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 &= ~LB_D4_VLINE_INTERRUPT;
6634 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D4 vline\n");
6635
6636 break;
6637 default:
6638 DRM_DEBUG("Unhandled interrupt: %d %d\n", src_id, src_data);
6639 break;
6640 }
6641 break;
6642 case 5: /* D5 vblank/vline */
6643 switch (src_data) {
6644 case 0: /* D5 vblank */
6645 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont4 & LB_D5_VBLANK_INTERRUPT))
6646 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6647
6648 if (rdev->irq.crtc_vblank_int[4]) {
6649 drm_handle_vblank(rdev->ddev, 4);
6650#ifdef __NetBSD__
6651 spin_lock(&rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6652 rdev->pm.vblank_sync = true;
6653 DRM_SPIN_WAKEUP_ONE(&rdev->irq.vblank_queue, &rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6654 spin_unlock(&rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6655#else
6656 rdev->pm.vblank_sync = true;
6657 wake_up(&rdev->irq.vblank_queue);
6658#endif
6659 }
6660 if (atomic_read(&rdev->irq.pflip[4]))
6661 radeon_crtc_handle_vblank(rdev, 4);
6662 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont4 &= ~LB_D5_VBLANK_INTERRUPT;
6663 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D5 vblank\n");
6664
6665 break;
6666 case 1: /* D5 vline */
6667 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont4 & LB_D5_VLINE_INTERRUPT))
6668 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6669
6670 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont4 &= ~LB_D5_VLINE_INTERRUPT;
6671 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D5 vline\n");
6672
6673 break;
6674 default:
6675 DRM_DEBUG("Unhandled interrupt: %d %d\n", src_id, src_data);
6676 break;
6677 }
6678 break;
6679 case 6: /* D6 vblank/vline */
6680 switch (src_data) {
6681 case 0: /* D6 vblank */
6682 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont5 & LB_D6_VBLANK_INTERRUPT))
6683 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6684
6685 if (rdev->irq.crtc_vblank_int[5]) {
6686 drm_handle_vblank(rdev->ddev, 5);
6687#ifdef __NetBSD__
6688 spin_lock(&rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6689 rdev->pm.vblank_sync = true;
6690 DRM_SPIN_WAKEUP_ONE(&rdev->irq.vblank_queue, &rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6691 spin_unlock(&rdev->irq.vblank_lock);
6692#else
6693 rdev->pm.vblank_sync = true;
6694 wake_up(&rdev->irq.vblank_queue);
6695#endif
6696 }
6697 if (atomic_read(&rdev->irq.pflip[5]))
6698 radeon_crtc_handle_vblank(rdev, 5);
6699 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont5 &= ~LB_D6_VBLANK_INTERRUPT;
6700 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D6 vblank\n");
6701
6702 break;
6703 case 1: /* D6 vline */
6704 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont5 & LB_D6_VLINE_INTERRUPT))
6705 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6706
6707 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont5 &= ~LB_D6_VLINE_INTERRUPT;
6708 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D6 vline\n");
6709
6710 break;
6711 default:
6712 DRM_DEBUG("Unhandled interrupt: %d %d\n", src_id, src_data);
6713 break;
6714 }
6715 break;
6716 case 8: /* D1 page flip */
6717 case 10: /* D2 page flip */
6718 case 12: /* D3 page flip */
6719 case 14: /* D4 page flip */
6720 case 16: /* D5 page flip */
6721 case 18: /* D6 page flip */
6722 DRM_DEBUG("IH: D%d flip\n", ((src_id - 8) >> 1) + 1);
6723 if (radeon_use_pflipirq > 0)
6724 radeon_crtc_handle_flip(rdev, (src_id - 8) >> 1);
6725 break;
6726 case 42: /* HPD hotplug */
6727 switch (src_data) {
6728 case 0:
6729 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int & DC_HPD1_INTERRUPT))
6730 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6731
6732 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int &= ~DC_HPD1_INTERRUPT;
6733 queue_hotplug = true;
6734 DRM_DEBUG("IH: HPD1\n");
6735
6736 break;
6737 case 1:
6738 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont & DC_HPD2_INTERRUPT))
6739 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6740
6741 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont &= ~DC_HPD2_INTERRUPT;
6742 queue_hotplug = true;
6743 DRM_DEBUG("IH: HPD2\n");
6744
6745 break;
6746 case 2:
6747 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 & DC_HPD3_INTERRUPT))
6748 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6749
6750 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 &= ~DC_HPD3_INTERRUPT;
6751 queue_hotplug = true;
6752 DRM_DEBUG("IH: HPD3\n");
6753
6754 break;
6755 case 3:
6756 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 & DC_HPD4_INTERRUPT))
6757 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6758
6759 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 &= ~DC_HPD4_INTERRUPT;
6760 queue_hotplug = true;
6761 DRM_DEBUG("IH: HPD4\n");
6762
6763 break;
6764 case 4:
6765 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont4 & DC_HPD5_INTERRUPT))
6766 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6767
6768 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont4 &= ~DC_HPD5_INTERRUPT;
6769 queue_hotplug = true;
6770 DRM_DEBUG("IH: HPD5\n");
6771
6772 break;
6773 case 5:
6774 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont5 & DC_HPD6_INTERRUPT))
6775 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6776
6777 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont5 &= ~DC_HPD6_INTERRUPT;
6778 queue_hotplug = true;
6779 DRM_DEBUG("IH: HPD6\n");
6780
6781 break;
6782 case 6:
6783 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int & DC_HPD1_RX_INTERRUPT))
6784 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6785
6786 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int &= ~DC_HPD1_RX_INTERRUPT;
6787 queue_dp = true;
6788 DRM_DEBUG("IH: HPD_RX 1\n");
6789
6790 break;
6791 case 7:
6792 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont & DC_HPD2_RX_INTERRUPT))
6793 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6794
6795 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont &= ~DC_HPD2_RX_INTERRUPT;
6796 queue_dp = true;
6797 DRM_DEBUG("IH: HPD_RX 2\n");
6798
6799 break;
6800 case 8:
6801 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 & DC_HPD3_RX_INTERRUPT))
6802 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6803
6804 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont2 &= ~DC_HPD3_RX_INTERRUPT;
6805 queue_dp = true;
6806 DRM_DEBUG("IH: HPD_RX 3\n");
6807
6808 break;
6809 case 9:
6810 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 & DC_HPD4_RX_INTERRUPT))
6811 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");
6812
6813 rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont3 &= ~DC_HPD4_RX_INTERRUPT;
6814 queue_dp = true;
6815 DRM_DEBUG("IH: HPD_RX 4\n");
6816
6817 break;
6818 case 10:
6819 if (!(rdev->irq.stat_regs.evergreen.disp_int_cont4 & DC_HPD5_RX_INTERRUPT))
6820 DRM_DEBUG("IH: IH event w/o asserted irq bit?\n");

6835 break;
6836 default:
6837 DRM_DEBUG("Unhandled interrupt: %d %d\n", src_id, src_data);
6838 break;
6839 }
6840 break;
6841 case 96:
6842 DRM_ERROR("SRBM_READ_ERROR: 0x%x\n", RREG32(SRBM_READ_ERROR));
6843 WREG32(SRBM_INT_ACK, 0x1);
6844 break;
6845 case 124: /* UVD */
6846 DRM_DEBUG("IH: UVD int: 0x%08x\n", src_data);
6847 radeon_fence_process(rdev, R600_RING_TYPE_UVD_INDEX);
6848 break;
6849 case 146:
6850 case 147:
6851 addr = RREG32(VM_CONTEXT1_PROTECTION_FAULT_ADDR);
6852 status = RREG32(VM_CONTEXT1_PROTECTION_FAULT_STATUS);
6853 /* reset addr and status */
6854 WREG32_P(VM_CONTEXT1_CNTL2, 1, ~1);
6855 if (addr == 0x0 && status == 0x0)
6856 break;
6857 dev_err(rdev->dev, "GPU fault detected: %d 0x%08x\n", src_id, src_data);
6858 dev_err(rdev->dev, " VM_CONTEXT1_PROTECTION_FAULT_ADDR 0x%08X\n",
6859 addr);
6860 dev_err(rdev->dev, " VM_CONTEXT1_PROTECTION_FAULT_STATUS 0x%08X\n",
6861 status);
6862 si_vm_decode_fault(rdev, status, addr);
6863 break;
6864 case 176: /* RINGID0 CP_INT */
6865 radeon_fence_process(rdev, RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX);
6866 break;
6867 case 177: /* RINGID1 CP_INT */
6868 radeon_fence_process(rdev, CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX);
6869 break;
6870 case 178: /* RINGID2 CP_INT */
6871 radeon_fence_process(rdev, CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX);
6872 break;
6873 case 181: /* CP EOP event */
6874 DRM_DEBUG("IH: CP EOP\n");
6875 switch (ring_id) {
6876 case 0:
6877 radeon_fence_process(rdev, RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX);
6878 break;
6879 case 1:
6880 radeon_fence_process(rdev, CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX);
6881 break;
6882 case 2:
6883 radeon_fence_process(rdev, CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX);
6884 break;
6885 }
6886 break;
6887 case 224: /* DMA trap event */
6888 DRM_DEBUG("IH: DMA trap\n");
6889 radeon_fence_process(rdev, R600_RING_TYPE_DMA_INDEX);
6890 break;
6891 case 230: /* thermal low to high */
6892 DRM_DEBUG("IH: thermal low to high\n");
6893 rdev->pm.dpm.thermal.high_to_low = false;
6894 queue_thermal = true;
6895 break;
6896 case 231: /* thermal high to low */
6897 DRM_DEBUG("IH: thermal high to low\n");
6898 rdev->pm.dpm.thermal.high_to_low = true;
6899 queue_thermal = true;
6900 break;
6901 case 233: /* GUI IDLE */
6902 DRM_DEBUG("IH: GUI idle\n");
6903 break;
6904 case 244: /* DMA trap event */
6905 DRM_DEBUG("IH: DMA1 trap\n");
6906 radeon_fence_process(rdev, CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_DMA1_INDEX);
6907 break;
6908 default:
6909 DRM_DEBUG("Unhandled interrupt: %d %d\n", src_id, src_data);
6910 break;
6911 }
6912
6913 /* wptr/rptr are in bytes! */
6914 rptr += 16;
6915 rptr &= rdev->ih.ptr_mask;
6916 WREG32(IH_RB_RPTR, rptr);
6917 }
6918 if (queue_dp)
6919 schedule_work(&rdev->dp_work);
6920 if (queue_hotplug)
6921 schedule_delayed_work(&rdev->hotplug_work, 0);
6922 if (queue_thermal && rdev->pm.dpm_enabled)
6923 schedule_work(&rdev->pm.dpm.thermal.work);
6924 rdev->ih.rptr = rptr;
6925 atomic_set(&rdev->ih.lock, 0);
6926
6927 /* make sure wptr hasn't changed while processing */
6928 wptr = si_get_ih_wptr(rdev);
6929 if (wptr != rptr)
6930 goto restart_ih;
6931
6932 return IRQ_HANDLED;
6933}
6934
6935/*
6936 * startup/shutdown callbacks
6937 */
6938static int si_startup(struct radeon_device *rdev)
6939{
6940 struct radeon_ring *ring;
6941 int r;
6942
6943 /* enable pcie gen2/3 link */
6944 si_pcie_gen3_enable(rdev);
6945 /* enable aspm */
6946 si_program_aspm(rdev);
6947
6948 /* scratch needs to be initialized before MC */
6949 r = r600_vram_scratch_init(rdev);
6950 if (r)
6951 return r;
6952
6953 si_mc_program(rdev);
6954
6955 if (!rdev->pm.dpm_enabled) {
6956 r = si_mc_load_microcode(rdev);
6957 if (r) {
6958 DRM_ERROR("Failed to load MC firmware!\n");
6959 return r;
6960 }
6961 }
6962
6963 r = si_pcie_gart_enable(rdev);
6964 if (r)
6965 return r;
6966 si_gpu_init(rdev);
6967
6968 /* allocate rlc buffers */
6969 if (rdev->family == CHIP_VERDE) {
6970 rdev->rlc.reg_list = verde_rlc_save_restore_register_list;
6971 rdev->rlc.reg_list_size =
6972 (u32)ARRAY_SIZE(verde_rlc_save_restore_register_list);
6973 }
6974 rdev->rlc.cs_data = si_cs_data;
6975 r = sumo_rlc_init(rdev);
6976 if (r) {
6977 DRM_ERROR("Failed to init rlc BOs!\n");
6978 return r;
6979 }
6980
6981 /* allocate wb buffer */
6982 r = radeon_wb_init(rdev);
6983 if (r)
6984 return r;
6985
6986 r = radeon_fence_driver_start_ring(rdev, RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX);
6987 if (r) {
6988 dev_err(rdev->dev, "failed initializing CP fences (%d).\n", r);
6989 return r;
6990 }
6991
6992 r = radeon_fence_driver_start_ring(rdev, CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX);
6993 if (r) {
6994 dev_err(rdev->dev, "failed initializing CP fences (%d).\n", r);
6995 return r;
6996 }
6997
6998 r = radeon_fence_driver_start_ring(rdev, CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX);
6999 if (r) {
7000 dev_err(rdev->dev, "failed initializing CP fences (%d).\n", r);
7001 return r;
7002 }
7003
7004 r = radeon_fence_driver_start_ring(rdev, R600_RING_TYPE_DMA_INDEX);
7005 if (r) {
7006 dev_err(rdev->dev, "failed initializing DMA fences (%d).\n", r);
7007 return r;
7008 }
7009
7010 r = radeon_fence_driver_start_ring(rdev, CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_DMA1_INDEX);
7011 if (r) {
7012 dev_err(rdev->dev, "failed initializing DMA fences (%d).\n", r);
7013 return r;
7014 }
7015
7016 if (rdev->has_uvd) {
7017 r = uvd_v2_2_resume(rdev);
7018 if (!r) {
7019 r = radeon_fence_driver_start_ring(rdev,
7020 R600_RING_TYPE_UVD_INDEX);
7021 if (r)
7022 dev_err(rdev->dev, "UVD fences init error (%d).\n", r);
7023 }
7024 if (r)
7025 rdev->ring[R600_RING_TYPE_UVD_INDEX].ring_size = 0;
7026 }
7027
7028 r = radeon_vce_resume(rdev);
7029 if (!r) {
7030 r = vce_v1_0_resume(rdev);
7031 if (!r)
7032 r = radeon_fence_driver_start_ring(rdev,
7033 TN_RING_TYPE_VCE1_INDEX);
7034 if (!r)
7035 r = radeon_fence_driver_start_ring(rdev,
7036 TN_RING_TYPE_VCE2_INDEX);
7037 }
7038 if (r) {
7039 dev_err(rdev->dev, "VCE init error (%d).\n", r);
7040 rdev->ring[TN_RING_TYPE_VCE1_INDEX].ring_size = 0;
7041 rdev->ring[TN_RING_TYPE_VCE2_INDEX].ring_size = 0;
7042 }
7043
7044 /* Enable IRQ */
7045 if (!rdev->irq.installed) {
7046 r = radeon_irq_kms_init(rdev);
7047 if (r)
7048 return r;
7049 }
7050
7051 r = si_irq_init(rdev);
7052 if (r) {
7053 DRM_ERROR("radeon: IH init failed (%d).\n", r);
7054 radeon_irq_kms_fini(rdev);
7055 return r;
7056 }
7057 si_irq_set(rdev);
7058
7059 ring = &rdev->ring[RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX];
7060 r = radeon_ring_init(rdev, ring, ring->ring_size, RADEON_WB_CP_RPTR_OFFSET,
7061 RADEON_CP_PACKET2);
7062 if (r)
7063 return r;
7064
7065 ring = &rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX];
7066 r = radeon_ring_init(rdev, ring, ring->ring_size, RADEON_WB_CP1_RPTR_OFFSET,
7067 RADEON_CP_PACKET2);
7068 if (r)
7069 return r;
7070
7071 ring = &rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX];
7072 r = radeon_ring_init(rdev, ring, ring->ring_size, RADEON_WB_CP2_RPTR_OFFSET,
7073 RADEON_CP_PACKET2);
7074 if (r)
7075 return r;
7076
7077 ring = &rdev->ring[R600_RING_TYPE_DMA_INDEX];
7078 r = radeon_ring_init(rdev, ring, ring->ring_size, R600_WB_DMA_RPTR_OFFSET,
7079 DMA_PACKET(DMA_PACKET_NOP, 0, 0, 0, 0));
7080 if (r)
7081 return r;
7082
7083 ring = &rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_DMA1_INDEX];
7084 r = radeon_ring_init(rdev, ring, ring->ring_size, CAYMAN_WB_DMA1_RPTR_OFFSET,
7085 DMA_PACKET(DMA_PACKET_NOP, 0, 0, 0, 0));
7086 if (r)
7087 return r;
7088
7089 r = si_cp_load_microcode(rdev);
7090 if (r)
7091 return r;
7092 r = si_cp_resume(rdev);
7093 if (r)
7094 return r;
7095
7096 r = cayman_dma_resume(rdev);
7097 if (r)
7098 return r;
7099
7100 if (rdev->has_uvd) {
7101 ring = &rdev->ring[R600_RING_TYPE_UVD_INDEX];
7102 if (ring->ring_size) {
7103 r = radeon_ring_init(rdev, ring, ring->ring_size, 0,
7104 RADEON_CP_PACKET2);
7105 if (!r)
7106 r = uvd_v1_0_init(rdev);
7107 if (r)
7108 DRM_ERROR("radeon: failed initializing UVD (%d).\n", r);
7109 }
7110 }
7111
7112 r = -ENOENT;
7113
7114 ring = &rdev->ring[TN_RING_TYPE_VCE1_INDEX];
7115 if (ring->ring_size)
7116 r = radeon_ring_init(rdev, ring, ring->ring_size, 0,
7117 VCE_CMD_NO_OP);
7118
7119 ring = &rdev->ring[TN_RING_TYPE_VCE2_INDEX];
7120 if (ring->ring_size)
7121 r = radeon_ring_init(rdev, ring, ring->ring_size, 0,
7122 VCE_CMD_NO_OP);
7123
7124 if (!r)
7125 r = vce_v1_0_init(rdev);
7126 else if (r != -ENOENT)
7127 DRM_ERROR("radeon: failed initializing VCE (%d).\n", r);
7128
7129 r = radeon_ib_pool_init(rdev);
7130 if (r) {
7131 dev_err(rdev->dev, "IB initialization failed (%d).\n", r);
7132 return r;
7133 }
7134
7135 r = radeon_vm_manager_init(rdev);
7136 if (r) {
7137 dev_err(rdev->dev, "vm manager initialization failed (%d).\n", r);
7138 return r;
7139 }
7140
7141 r = radeon_audio_init(rdev);
7142 if (r)
7143 return r;
7144
7145 return 0;
7146}
7147
7148int si_resume(struct radeon_device *rdev)
7149{
7150 int r;
7151
7152 /* Do not reset GPU before posting, on rv770 hw unlike on r500 hw,
7153 * posting will perform necessary task to bring back GPU into good
7154 * shape.
7155 */
7156 /* post card */
7157 atom_asic_init(rdev->mode_info.atom_context);
7158
7159 /* init golden registers */
7160 si_init_golden_registers(rdev);
7161
7162 if (rdev->pm.pm_method == PM_METHOD_DPM)
7163 radeon_pm_resume(rdev);
7164
7165 rdev->accel_working = true;
7166 r = si_startup(rdev);
7167 if (r) {
7168 DRM_ERROR("si startup failed on resume\n");
7169 rdev->accel_working = false;
7170 return r;
7171 }
7172
7173 return r;
7174
7175}
7176
7177int si_suspend(struct radeon_device *rdev)
7178{
7179 radeon_pm_suspend(rdev);
7180 radeon_audio_fini(rdev);
7181 radeon_vm_manager_fini(rdev);
7182 si_cp_enable(rdev, false);
7183 cayman_dma_stop(rdev);
7184 if (rdev->has_uvd) {
7185 uvd_v1_0_fini(rdev);
7186 radeon_uvd_suspend(rdev);
7187 radeon_vce_suspend(rdev);
7188 }
7189 si_fini_pg(rdev);
7190 si_fini_cg(rdev);
7191 si_irq_suspend(rdev);
7192 radeon_wb_disable(rdev);
7193 si_pcie_gart_disable(rdev);
7194 return 0;
7195}
7196
7197/* Plan is to move initialization in that function and use
7198 * helper function so that radeon_device_init pretty much
7199 * do nothing more than calling asic specific function. This
7200 * should also allow to remove a bunch of callback function
7201 * like vram_info.
7202 */
7203int si_init(struct radeon_device *rdev)
7204{
7205 struct radeon_ring *ring = &rdev->ring[RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX];
7206 int r;
7207
7208 /* Read BIOS */
7209 if (!radeon_get_bios(rdev)) {
7210 if (ASIC_IS_AVIVO(rdev))
7211 return -EINVAL;
7212 }
7213 /* Must be an ATOMBIOS */
7214 if (!rdev->is_atom_bios) {
7215 dev_err(rdev->dev, "Expecting atombios for cayman GPU\n");
7216 return -EINVAL;
7217 }
7218 r = radeon_atombios_init(rdev);
7219 if (r)
7220 return r;
7221
7222 /* Post card if necessary */
7223 if (!radeon_card_posted(rdev)) {
7224 if (!rdev->bios) {
7225 dev_err(rdev->dev, "Card not posted and no BIOS - ignoring\n");
7226 return -EINVAL;
7227 }
7228 DRM_INFO("GPU not posted. posting now...\n");
7229 atom_asic_init(rdev->mode_info.atom_context);
7230 }
7231 /* init golden registers */
7232 si_init_golden_registers(rdev);
7233 /* Initialize scratch registers */
7234 si_scratch_init(rdev);
7235 /* Initialize surface registers */
7236 radeon_surface_init(rdev);
7237 /* Initialize clocks */
7238 radeon_get_clock_info(rdev->ddev);
7239
7240 /* Fence driver */
7241 r = radeon_fence_driver_init(rdev);
7242 if (r)
7243 return r;
7244
7245 /* initialize memory controller */
7246 r = si_mc_init(rdev);
7247 if (r)
7248 return r;
7249 /* Memory manager */
7250 r = radeon_bo_init(rdev);
7251 if (r)
7252 return r;
7253
7254 if (!rdev->me_fw || !rdev->pfp_fw || !rdev->ce_fw ||
7255 !rdev->rlc_fw || !rdev->mc_fw) {
7256 r = si_init_microcode(rdev);
7257 if (r) {
7258 DRM_ERROR("Failed to load firmware!\n");
7259 return r;
7260 }
7261 }
7262
7263 /* Initialize power management */
7264 radeon_pm_init(rdev);
7265
7266 ring = &rdev->ring[RADEON_RING_TYPE_GFX_INDEX];
7267 ring->ring_obj = NULL;
7268 r600_ring_init(rdev, ring, 1024 * 1024);
7269
7270 ring = &rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP1_INDEX];
7271 ring->ring_obj = NULL;
7272 r600_ring_init(rdev, ring, 1024 * 1024);
7273
7274 ring = &rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_CP2_INDEX];
7275 ring->ring_obj = NULL;
7276 r600_ring_init(rdev, ring, 1024 * 1024);
7277
7278 ring = &rdev->ring[R600_RING_TYPE_DMA_INDEX];
7279 ring->ring_obj = NULL;
7280 r600_ring_init(rdev, ring, 64 * 1024);
7281
7282 ring = &rdev->ring[CAYMAN_RING_TYPE_DMA1_INDEX];
7283 ring->ring_obj = NULL;
7284 r600_ring_init(rdev, ring, 64 * 1024);
7285
7286 if (rdev->has_uvd) {
7287 r = radeon_uvd_init(rdev);
7288 if (!r) {
7289 ring = &rdev->ring[R600_RING_TYPE_UVD_INDEX];
7290 ring->ring_obj = NULL;
7291 r600_ring_init(rdev, ring, 4096);
7292 }
7293 }
7294
7295 r = radeon_vce_init(rdev);
7296 if (!r) {
7297 ring = &rdev->ring[TN_RING_TYPE_VCE1_INDEX];
7298 ring->ring_obj = NULL;
7299 r600_ring_init(rdev, ring, 4096);
7300
7301 ring = &rdev->ring[TN_RING_TYPE_VCE2_INDEX];
7302 ring->ring_obj = NULL;
7303 r600_ring_init(rdev, ring, 4096);
7304 }
7305
7306 rdev->ih.ring_obj = NULL;
7307 r600_ih_ring_init(rdev, 64 * 1024);
7308
7309 r = r600_pcie_gart_init(rdev);
7310 if (r)
7311 return r;
7312
7313 rdev->accel_working = true;
7314 r = si_startup(rdev);
7315 if (r) {
7316 dev_err(rdev->dev, "disabling GPU acceleration\n");
7317 si_cp_fini(rdev);
7318 cayman_dma_fini(rdev);
7319 si_irq_fini(rdev);
7320 sumo_rlc_fini(rdev);
7321 radeon_wb_fini(rdev);
7322 radeon_ib_pool_fini(rdev);
7323 radeon_vm_manager_fini(rdev);
7324 radeon_irq_kms_fini(rdev);
7325 si_pcie_gart_fini(rdev);
7326 rdev->accel_working = false;
7327 }
7328
7329 /* Don't start up if the MC ucode is missing.
7330 * The default clocks and voltages before the MC ucode
7331 * is loaded are not suffient for advanced operations.
7332 */
7333 if (!rdev->mc_fw) {
7334 DRM_ERROR("radeon: MC ucode required for NI+.\n");
7335 return -EINVAL;
7336 }
7337
7338 return 0;
7339}
7340
7341void si_fini(struct radeon_device *rdev)
7342{
7343 radeon_pm_fini(rdev);
7344 si_cp_fini(rdev);
7345 cayman_dma_fini(rdev);
7346 si_fini_pg(rdev);
7347 si_fini_cg(rdev);
7348 si_irq_fini(rdev);
7349 sumo_rlc_fini(rdev);
7350 radeon_wb_fini(rdev);
7351 radeon_vm_manager_fini(rdev);
7352 radeon_ib_pool_fini(rdev);
7353 radeon_irq_kms_fini(rdev);
7354 if (rdev->has_uvd) {
7355 uvd_v1_0_fini(rdev);
7356 radeon_uvd_fini(rdev);
7357 radeon_vce_fini(rdev);
7358 }
7359 si_pcie_gart_fini(rdev);
7360 r600_vram_scratch_fini(rdev);
7361 radeon_gem_fini(rdev);
7362 radeon_fence_driver_fini(rdev);
7363 radeon_bo_fini(rdev);
7364 radeon_atombios_fini(rdev);
7365 kfree(rdev->bios);
7366 rdev->bios = NULL;
7367}
7368
7369/**
7370 * si_get_gpu_clock_counter - return GPU clock counter snapshot
7371 *
7372 * @rdev: radeon_device pointer
7373 *
7374 * Fetches a GPU clock counter snapshot (SI).
7375 * Returns the 64 bit clock counter snapshot.
7376 */
7377uint64_t si_get_gpu_clock_counter(struct radeon_device *rdev)
7378{
7379 uint64_t clock;
7380
7381 mutex_lock(&rdev->gpu_clock_mutex);
7382 WREG32(RLC_CAPTURE_GPU_CLOCK_COUNT, 1);
7383 clock = (uint64_t)RREG32(RLC_GPU_CLOCK_COUNT_LSB) |
7384 ((uint64_t)RREG32(RLC_GPU_CLOCK_COUNT_MSB) << 32ULL);
7385 mutex_unlock(&rdev->gpu_clock_mutex);
7386 return clock;
7387}
7388
7389int si_set_uvd_clocks(struct radeon_device *rdev, u32 vclk, u32 dclk)
7390{
7391 unsigned fb_div = 0, vclk_div = 0, dclk_div = 0;
7392 int r;
7393
7394 /* bypass vclk and dclk with bclk */
7395 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL_2,
7396 VCLK_SRC_SEL(1) | DCLK_SRC_SEL(1),
7397 ~(VCLK_SRC_SEL_MASK | DCLK_SRC_SEL_MASK));
7398
7399 /* put PLL in bypass mode */
7400 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL, UPLL_BYPASS_EN_MASK, ~UPLL_BYPASS_EN_MASK);
7401
7402 if (!vclk || !dclk) {
7403 /* keep the Bypass mode */
7404 return 0;
7405 }
7406
7407 r = radeon_uvd_calc_upll_dividers(rdev, vclk, dclk, 125000, 250000,
7408 16384, 0x03FFFFFF, 0, 128, 5,
7409 &fb_div, &vclk_div, &dclk_div);
7410 if (r)
7411 return r;
7412
7413 /* set RESET_ANTI_MUX to 0 */
7414 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL_5, 0, ~RESET_ANTI_MUX_MASK);
7415
7416 /* set VCO_MODE to 1 */
7417 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL, UPLL_VCO_MODE_MASK, ~UPLL_VCO_MODE_MASK);
7418
7419 /* disable sleep mode */
7420 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL, 0, ~UPLL_SLEEP_MASK);
7421
7422 /* deassert UPLL_RESET */
7423 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL, 0, ~UPLL_RESET_MASK);
7424
7425 mdelay(1);
7426
7427 r = radeon_uvd_send_upll_ctlreq(rdev, CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL);
7428 if (r)
7429 return r;
7430
7431 /* assert UPLL_RESET again */
7432 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL, UPLL_RESET_MASK, ~UPLL_RESET_MASK);
7433
7434 /* disable spread spectrum. */
7435 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_SPREAD_SPECTRUM, 0, ~SSEN_MASK);
7436
7437 /* set feedback divider */
7438 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL_3, UPLL_FB_DIV(fb_div), ~UPLL_FB_DIV_MASK);
7439
7440 /* set ref divider to 0 */
7441 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL, 0, ~UPLL_REF_DIV_MASK);
7442
7443 if (fb_div < 307200)
7444 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL_4, 0, ~UPLL_SPARE_ISPARE9);
7445 else
7446 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL_4, UPLL_SPARE_ISPARE9, ~UPLL_SPARE_ISPARE9);
7447
7448 /* set PDIV_A and PDIV_B */
7449 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL_2,
7450 UPLL_PDIV_A(vclk_div) | UPLL_PDIV_B(dclk_div),
7451 ~(UPLL_PDIV_A_MASK | UPLL_PDIV_B_MASK));
7452
7453 /* give the PLL some time to settle */
7454 mdelay(15);
7455
7456 /* deassert PLL_RESET */
7457 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL, 0, ~UPLL_RESET_MASK);
7458
7459 mdelay(15);
7460
7461 /* switch from bypass mode to normal mode */
7462 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL, 0, ~UPLL_BYPASS_EN_MASK);
7463
7464 r = radeon_uvd_send_upll_ctlreq(rdev, CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL);
7465 if (r)
7466 return r;
7467
7468 /* switch VCLK and DCLK selection */
7469 WREG32_P(CG_UPLL_FUNC_CNTL_2,
7470 VCLK_SRC_SEL(2) | DCLK_SRC_SEL(2),
7471 ~(VCLK_SRC_SEL_MASK | DCLK_SRC_SEL_MASK));
7472
7473 mdelay(100);
7474
7475 return 0;
7476}
7477
7478static void si_pcie_gen3_enable(struct radeon_device *rdev)
7479{
7480#ifndef __NetBSD__ /* XXX radeon pcie */
7481 struct pci_dev *root = rdev->pdev->bus->self;
7482 int bridge_pos, gpu_pos;
7483 u32 speed_cntl, mask, current_data_rate;
7484 int ret, i;
7485 u16 tmp16;
7486
7487 if (pci_is_root_bus(rdev->pdev->bus))
7488 return;
7489
7490 if (radeon_pcie_gen2 == 0)
7491 return;
7492
7493 if (rdev->flags & RADEON_IS_IGP)
7494 return;
7495
7496 if (!(rdev->flags & RADEON_IS_PCIE))
7497 return;
7498
7499 ret = drm_pcie_get_speed_cap_mask(rdev->ddev, &mask);
7500 if (ret != 0)
7501 return;
7502
7503 if (!(mask & (DRM_PCIE_SPEED_50 | DRM_PCIE_SPEED_80)))
7504 return;
7505
7506 speed_cntl = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_SPEED_CNTL);
7507 current_data_rate = (speed_cntl & LC_CURRENT_DATA_RATE_MASK) >>
7508 LC_CURRENT_DATA_RATE_SHIFT;
7509 if (mask & DRM_PCIE_SPEED_80) {
7510 if (current_data_rate == 2) {
7511 DRM_INFO("PCIE gen 3 link speeds already enabled\n");
7512 return;
7513 }
7514 DRM_INFO("enabling PCIE gen 3 link speeds, disable with radeon.pcie_gen2=0\n");
7515 } else if (mask & DRM_PCIE_SPEED_50) {
7516 if (current_data_rate == 1) {
7517 DRM_INFO("PCIE gen 2 link speeds already enabled\n");
7518 return;
7519 }
7520 DRM_INFO("enabling PCIE gen 2 link speeds, disable with radeon.pcie_gen2=0\n");
7521 }
7522
7523 bridge_pos = pci_pcie_cap(root);
7524 if (!bridge_pos)
7525 return;
7526
7527 gpu_pos = pci_pcie_cap(rdev->pdev);
7528 if (!gpu_pos)
7529 return;
7530
7531 if (mask & DRM_PCIE_SPEED_80) {
7532 /* re-try equalization if gen3 is not already enabled */
7533 if (current_data_rate != 2) {
7534 u16 bridge_cfg, gpu_cfg;
7535 u16 bridge_cfg2, gpu_cfg2;
7536 u32 max_lw, current_lw, tmp;
7537
7538 pci_read_config_word(root, bridge_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL, &bridge_cfg);
7539 pci_read_config_word(rdev->pdev, gpu_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL, &gpu_cfg);
7540
7541 tmp16 = bridge_cfg | PCI_EXP_LNKCTL_HAWD;
7542 pci_write_config_word(root, bridge_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL, tmp16);
7543
7544 tmp16 = gpu_cfg | PCI_EXP_LNKCTL_HAWD;
7545 pci_write_config_word(rdev->pdev, gpu_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL, tmp16);
7546
7547 tmp = RREG32_PCIE(PCIE_LC_STATUS1);
7548 max_lw = (tmp & LC_DETECTED_LINK_WIDTH_MASK) >> LC_DETECTED_LINK_WIDTH_SHIFT;
7549 current_lw = (tmp & LC_OPERATING_LINK_WIDTH_MASK) >> LC_OPERATING_LINK_WIDTH_SHIFT;
7550
7551 if (current_lw < max_lw) {
7552 tmp = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_LINK_WIDTH_CNTL);
7553 if (tmp & LC_RENEGOTIATION_SUPPORT) {
7554 tmp &= ~(LC_LINK_WIDTH_MASK | LC_UPCONFIGURE_DIS);
7555 tmp |= (max_lw << LC_LINK_WIDTH_SHIFT);
7556 tmp |= LC_UPCONFIGURE_SUPPORT | LC_RENEGOTIATE_EN | LC_RECONFIG_NOW;
7557 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_LINK_WIDTH_CNTL, tmp);
7558 }
7559 }
7560
7561 for (i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
7562 /* check status */
7563 pci_read_config_word(rdev->pdev, gpu_pos + PCI_EXP_DEVSTA, &tmp16);
7564 if (tmp16 & PCI_EXP_DEVSTA_TRPND)
7565 break;
7566
7567 pci_read_config_word(root, bridge_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL, &bridge_cfg);
7568 pci_read_config_word(rdev->pdev, gpu_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL, &gpu_cfg);
7569
7570 pci_read_config_word(root, bridge_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL2, &bridge_cfg2);
7571 pci_read_config_word(rdev->pdev, gpu_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL2, &gpu_cfg2);
7572
7573 tmp = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL4);
7574 tmp |= LC_SET_QUIESCE;
7575 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL4, tmp);
7576
7577 tmp = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL4);
7578 tmp |= LC_REDO_EQ;
7579 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL4, tmp);
7580
7581 mdelay(100);
7582
7583 /* linkctl */
7584 pci_read_config_word(root, bridge_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL, &tmp16);
7585 tmp16 &= ~PCI_EXP_LNKCTL_HAWD;
7586 tmp16 |= (bridge_cfg & PCI_EXP_LNKCTL_HAWD);
7587 pci_write_config_word(root, bridge_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL, tmp16);
7588
7589 pci_read_config_word(rdev->pdev, gpu_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL, &tmp16);
7590 tmp16 &= ~PCI_EXP_LNKCTL_HAWD;
7591 tmp16 |= (gpu_cfg & PCI_EXP_LNKCTL_HAWD);
7592 pci_write_config_word(rdev->pdev, gpu_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL, tmp16);
7593
7594 /* linkctl2 */
7595 pci_read_config_word(root, bridge_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL2, &tmp16);
7596 tmp16 &= ~((1 << 4) | (7 << 9));
7597 tmp16 |= (bridge_cfg2 & ((1 << 4) | (7 << 9)));
7598 pci_write_config_word(root, bridge_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL2, tmp16);
7599
7600 pci_read_config_word(rdev->pdev, gpu_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL2, &tmp16);
7601 tmp16 &= ~((1 << 4) | (7 << 9));
7602 tmp16 |= (gpu_cfg2 & ((1 << 4) | (7 << 9)));
7603 pci_write_config_word(rdev->pdev, gpu_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL2, tmp16);
7604
7605 tmp = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL4);
7606 tmp &= ~LC_SET_QUIESCE;
7607 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL4, tmp);
7608 }
7609 }
7610 }
7611
7612 /* set the link speed */
7613 speed_cntl |= LC_FORCE_EN_SW_SPEED_CHANGE | LC_FORCE_DIS_HW_SPEED_CHANGE;
7614 speed_cntl &= ~LC_FORCE_DIS_SW_SPEED_CHANGE;
7615 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_SPEED_CNTL, speed_cntl);
7616
7617 pci_read_config_word(rdev->pdev, gpu_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL2, &tmp16);
7618 tmp16 &= ~0xf;
7619 if (mask & DRM_PCIE_SPEED_80)
7620 tmp16 |= 3; /* gen3 */
7621 else if (mask & DRM_PCIE_SPEED_50)
7622 tmp16 |= 2; /* gen2 */
7623 else
7624 tmp16 |= 1; /* gen1 */
7625 pci_write_config_word(rdev->pdev, gpu_pos + PCI_EXP_LNKCTL2, tmp16);
7626
7627 speed_cntl = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_SPEED_CNTL);
7628 speed_cntl |= LC_INITIATE_LINK_SPEED_CHANGE;
7629 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_SPEED_CNTL, speed_cntl);
7630
7631 for (i = 0; i < rdev->usec_timeout; i++) {
7632 speed_cntl = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_SPEED_CNTL);
7633 if ((speed_cntl & LC_INITIATE_LINK_SPEED_CHANGE) == 0)
7634 break;
7635 udelay(1);
7636 }
7637#endif
7638}
7639
7640static void si_program_aspm(struct radeon_device *rdev)
7641{
7642 u32 data, orig;
7643 bool disable_l0s = false, disable_l1 = false, disable_plloff_in_l1 = false;
7644 bool disable_clkreq = false;
7645
7646 if (radeon_aspm == 0)
7647 return;
7648
7649 if (!(rdev->flags & RADEON_IS_PCIE))
7650 return;
7651
7652 orig = data = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_N_FTS_CNTL);
7653 data &= ~LC_XMIT_N_FTS_MASK;
7654 data |= LC_XMIT_N_FTS(0x24) | LC_XMIT_N_FTS_OVERRIDE_EN;
7655 if (orig != data)
7656 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_N_FTS_CNTL, data);
7657
7658 orig = data = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL3);
7659 data |= LC_GO_TO_RECOVERY;
7660 if (orig != data)
7661 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL3, data);
7662
7663 orig = data = RREG32_PCIE(PCIE_P_CNTL);
7664 data |= P_IGNORE_EDB_ERR;
7665 if (orig != data)
7666 WREG32_PCIE(PCIE_P_CNTL, data);
7667
7668 orig = data = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL);
7669 data &= ~(LC_L0S_INACTIVITY_MASK | LC_L1_INACTIVITY_MASK);
7670 data |= LC_PMI_TO_L1_DIS;
7671 if (!disable_l0s)
7672 data |= LC_L0S_INACTIVITY(7);
7673
7674 if (!disable_l1) {
7675 data |= LC_L1_INACTIVITY(7);
7676 data &= ~LC_PMI_TO_L1_DIS;
7677 if (orig != data)
7678 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL, data);
7679
7680 if (!disable_plloff_in_l1) {
7681 bool clk_req_support;
7682
7683 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_PWRDOWN_0);
7684 data &= ~(PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_OFF_0_MASK | PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_TXS2_0_MASK);
7685 data |= PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_OFF_0(7) | PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_TXS2_0(7);
7686 if (orig != data)
7687 WREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_PWRDOWN_0, data);
7688
7689 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_PWRDOWN_1);
7690 data &= ~(PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_OFF_1_MASK | PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_TXS2_1_MASK);
7691 data |= PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_OFF_1(7) | PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_TXS2_1(7);
7692 if (orig != data)
7693 WREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_PWRDOWN_1, data);
7694
7695 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_PWRDOWN_0);
7696 data &= ~(PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_OFF_0_MASK | PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_TXS2_0_MASK);
7697 data |= PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_OFF_0(7) | PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_TXS2_0(7);
7698 if (orig != data)
7699 WREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_PWRDOWN_0, data);
7700
7701 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_PWRDOWN_1);
7702 data &= ~(PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_OFF_1_MASK | PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_TXS2_1_MASK);
7703 data |= PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_OFF_1(7) | PLL_POWER_STATE_IN_TXS2_1(7);
7704 if (orig != data)
7705 WREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_PWRDOWN_1, data);
7706
7707 if ((rdev->family != CHIP_OLAND) && (rdev->family != CHIP_HAINAN)) {
7708 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_PWRDOWN_0);
7709 data &= ~PLL_RAMP_UP_TIME_0_MASK;
7710 if (orig != data)
7711 WREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_PWRDOWN_0, data);
7712
7713 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_PWRDOWN_1);
7714 data &= ~PLL_RAMP_UP_TIME_1_MASK;
7715 if (orig != data)
7716 WREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_PWRDOWN_1, data);
7717
7718 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_PWRDOWN_2);
7719 data &= ~PLL_RAMP_UP_TIME_2_MASK;
7720 if (orig != data)
7721 WREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_PWRDOWN_2, data);
7722
7723 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_PWRDOWN_3);
7724 data &= ~PLL_RAMP_UP_TIME_3_MASK;
7725 if (orig != data)
7726 WREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_PWRDOWN_3, data);
7727
7728 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_PWRDOWN_0);
7729 data &= ~PLL_RAMP_UP_TIME_0_MASK;
7730 if (orig != data)
7731 WREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_PWRDOWN_0, data);
7732
7733 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_PWRDOWN_1);
7734 data &= ~PLL_RAMP_UP_TIME_1_MASK;
7735 if (orig != data)
7736 WREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_PWRDOWN_1, data);
7737
7738 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_PWRDOWN_2);
7739 data &= ~PLL_RAMP_UP_TIME_2_MASK;
7740 if (orig != data)
7741 WREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_PWRDOWN_2, data);
7742
7743 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_PWRDOWN_3);
7744 data &= ~PLL_RAMP_UP_TIME_3_MASK;
7745 if (orig != data)
7746 WREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_PWRDOWN_3, data);
7747 }
7748 orig = data = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_LINK_WIDTH_CNTL);
7749 data &= ~LC_DYN_LANES_PWR_STATE_MASK;
7750 data |= LC_DYN_LANES_PWR_STATE(3);
7751 if (orig != data)
7752 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_LINK_WIDTH_CNTL, data);
7753
7754 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_CNTL);
7755 data &= ~LS2_EXIT_TIME_MASK;
7756 if ((rdev->family == CHIP_OLAND) || (rdev->family == CHIP_HAINAN))
7757 data |= LS2_EXIT_TIME(5);
7758 if (orig != data)
7759 WREG32_PIF_PHY0(PB0_PIF_CNTL, data);
7760
7761 orig = data = RREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_CNTL);
7762 data &= ~LS2_EXIT_TIME_MASK;
7763 if ((rdev->family == CHIP_OLAND) || (rdev->family == CHIP_HAINAN))
7764 data |= LS2_EXIT_TIME(5);
7765 if (orig != data)
7766 WREG32_PIF_PHY1(PB1_PIF_CNTL, data);
7767
7768 if (!disable_clkreq &&
7769 !pci_is_root_bus(rdev->pdev->bus)) {
7770#ifndef __NetBSD__ /* XXX radeon pcie */
7771 struct pci_dev *root = rdev->pdev->bus->self;
7772 u32 lnkcap;
7773#endif
7774
7775 clk_req_support = false;
7776#ifndef __NetBSD__ /* XXX radeon pcie */
7777 pcie_capability_read_dword(root, PCI_EXP_LNKCAP, &lnkcap);
7778 if (lnkcap & PCI_EXP_LNKCAP_CLKPM)
7779 clk_req_support = true;
7780#endif
7781 } else {
7782 clk_req_support = false;
7783 }
7784
7785 if (clk_req_support) {
7786 orig = data = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL2);
7787 data |= LC_ALLOW_PDWN_IN_L1 | LC_ALLOW_PDWN_IN_L23;
7788 if (orig != data)
7789 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL2, data);
7790
7791 orig = data = RREG32(THM_CLK_CNTL);
7792 data &= ~(CMON_CLK_SEL_MASK | TMON_CLK_SEL_MASK);
7793 data |= CMON_CLK_SEL(1) | TMON_CLK_SEL(1);
7794 if (orig != data)
7795 WREG32(THM_CLK_CNTL, data);
7796
7797 orig = data = RREG32(MISC_CLK_CNTL);
7798 data &= ~(DEEP_SLEEP_CLK_SEL_MASK | ZCLK_SEL_MASK);
7799 data |= DEEP_SLEEP_CLK_SEL(1) | ZCLK_SEL(1);
7800 if (orig != data)
7801 WREG32(MISC_CLK_CNTL, data);
7802
7803 orig = data = RREG32(CG_CLKPIN_CNTL);
7804 data &= ~BCLK_AS_XCLK;
7805 if (orig != data)
7806 WREG32(CG_CLKPIN_CNTL, data);
7807
7808 orig = data = RREG32(CG_CLKPIN_CNTL_2);
7809 data &= ~FORCE_BIF_REFCLK_EN;
7810 if (orig != data)
7811 WREG32(CG_CLKPIN_CNTL_2, data);
7812
7813 orig = data = RREG32(MPLL_BYPASSCLK_SEL);
7814 data &= ~MPLL_CLKOUT_SEL_MASK;
7815 data |= MPLL_CLKOUT_SEL(4);
7816 if (orig != data)
7817 WREG32(MPLL_BYPASSCLK_SEL, data);
7818
7819 orig = data = RREG32(SPLL_CNTL_MODE);
7820 data &= ~SPLL_REFCLK_SEL_MASK;
7821 if (orig != data)
7822 WREG32(SPLL_CNTL_MODE, data);
7823 }
7824 }
7825 } else {
7826 if (orig != data)
7827 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL, data);
7828 }
7829
7830 orig = data = RREG32_PCIE(PCIE_CNTL2);
7831 data |= SLV_MEM_LS_EN | MST_MEM_LS_EN | REPLAY_MEM_LS_EN;
7832 if (orig != data)
7833 WREG32_PCIE(PCIE_CNTL2, data);
7834
7835 if (!disable_l0s) {
7836 data = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_N_FTS_CNTL);
7837 if((data & LC_N_FTS_MASK) == LC_N_FTS_MASK) {
7838 data = RREG32_PCIE(PCIE_LC_STATUS1);
7839 if ((data & LC_REVERSE_XMIT) && (data & LC_REVERSE_RCVR)) {
7840 orig = data = RREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL);
7841 data &= ~LC_L0S_INACTIVITY_MASK;
7842 if (orig != data)
7843 WREG32_PCIE_PORT(PCIE_LC_CNTL, data);
7844 }
7845 }
7846 }
7847}
7848
7849int si_vce_send_vcepll_ctlreq(struct radeon_device *rdev)
7850{
7851 unsigned i;
7852
7853 /* make sure VCEPLL_CTLREQ is deasserted */
7854 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, 0, ~UPLL_CTLREQ_MASK);
7855
7856 mdelay(10);
7857
7858 /* assert UPLL_CTLREQ */
7859 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, UPLL_CTLREQ_MASK, ~UPLL_CTLREQ_MASK);
7860
7861 /* wait for CTLACK and CTLACK2 to get asserted */
7862 for (i = 0; i < 100; ++i) {
7863 uint32_t mask = UPLL_CTLACK_MASK | UPLL_CTLACK2_MASK;
7864 if ((RREG32_SMC(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL) & mask) == mask)
7865 break;
7866 mdelay(10);
7867 }
7868
7869 /* deassert UPLL_CTLREQ */
7870 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, 0, ~UPLL_CTLREQ_MASK);
7871
7872 if (i == 100) {
7873 DRM_ERROR("Timeout setting UVD clocks!\n");
7874 return -ETIMEDOUT;
7875 }
7876
7877 return 0;
7878}
7879
7880int si_set_vce_clocks(struct radeon_device *rdev, u32 evclk, u32 ecclk)
7881{
7882 unsigned fb_div = 0, evclk_div = 0, ecclk_div = 0;
7883 int r;
7884
7885 /* bypass evclk and ecclk with bclk */
7886 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL_2,
7887 EVCLK_SRC_SEL(1) | ECCLK_SRC_SEL(1),
7888 ~(EVCLK_SRC_SEL_MASK | ECCLK_SRC_SEL_MASK));
7889
7890 /* put PLL in bypass mode */
7891 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, VCEPLL_BYPASS_EN_MASK,
7892 ~VCEPLL_BYPASS_EN_MASK);
7893
7894 if (!evclk || !ecclk) {
7895 /* keep the Bypass mode, put PLL to sleep */
7896 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, VCEPLL_SLEEP_MASK,
7897 ~VCEPLL_SLEEP_MASK);
7898 return 0;
7899 }
7900
7901 r = radeon_uvd_calc_upll_dividers(rdev, evclk, ecclk, 125000, 250000,
7902 16384, 0x03FFFFFF, 0, 128, 5,
7903 &fb_div, &evclk_div, &ecclk_div);
7904 if (r)
7905 return r;
7906
7907 /* set RESET_ANTI_MUX to 0 */
7908 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL_5, 0, ~RESET_ANTI_MUX_MASK);
7909
7910 /* set VCO_MODE to 1 */
7911 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, VCEPLL_VCO_MODE_MASK,
7912 ~VCEPLL_VCO_MODE_MASK);
7913
7914 /* toggle VCEPLL_SLEEP to 1 then back to 0 */
7915 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, VCEPLL_SLEEP_MASK,
7916 ~VCEPLL_SLEEP_MASK);
7917 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, 0, ~VCEPLL_SLEEP_MASK);
7918
7919 /* deassert VCEPLL_RESET */
7920 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, 0, ~VCEPLL_RESET_MASK);
7921
7922 mdelay(1);
7923
7924 r = si_vce_send_vcepll_ctlreq(rdev);
7925 if (r)
7926 return r;
7927
7928 /* assert VCEPLL_RESET again */
7929 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, VCEPLL_RESET_MASK, ~VCEPLL_RESET_MASK);
7930
7931 /* disable spread spectrum. */
7932 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_SPREAD_SPECTRUM, 0, ~SSEN_MASK);
7933
7934 /* set feedback divider */
7935 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL_3, VCEPLL_FB_DIV(fb_div), ~VCEPLL_FB_DIV_MASK);
7936
7937 /* set ref divider to 0 */
7938 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, 0, ~VCEPLL_REF_DIV_MASK);
7939
7940 /* set PDIV_A and PDIV_B */
7941 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL_2,
7942 VCEPLL_PDIV_A(evclk_div) | VCEPLL_PDIV_B(ecclk_div),
7943 ~(VCEPLL_PDIV_A_MASK | VCEPLL_PDIV_B_MASK));
7944
7945 /* give the PLL some time to settle */
7946 mdelay(15);
7947
7948 /* deassert PLL_RESET */
7949 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, 0, ~VCEPLL_RESET_MASK);
7950
7951 mdelay(15);
7952
7953 /* switch from bypass mode to normal mode */
7954 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL, 0, ~VCEPLL_BYPASS_EN_MASK);
7955
7956 r = si_vce_send_vcepll_ctlreq(rdev);
7957 if (r)
7958 return r;
7959
7960 /* switch VCLK and DCLK selection */
7961 WREG32_SMC_P(CG_VCEPLL_FUNC_CNTL_2,
7962 EVCLK_SRC_SEL(16) | ECCLK_SRC_SEL(16),
7963 ~(EVCLK_SRC_SEL_MASK | ECCLK_SRC_SEL_MASK));
7964
7965 mdelay(100);
7966
7967 return 0;
7968}
